elegance-in-javascript-8b15c98a541b\">Composition and Currying Elegance in JavaScript &mdash; Pragyan Das</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://hackernoon.com/javascript-functional-composition-for-every-day-use-22421ef65a10\">Functional JavaScript: Function Composition For Every Day Use &mdash; Joel Thoms</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://medium.com/%40acparas/what-i-learned-today-july-2-2017-ab9a46dbf85f\">Functional Composition: compose() and pipe() &mdash; Anton Paras</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://busypeoples.github.io/post/functional-composing-javascript/\">Why The Hipsters Compose Everything: Functional Composing In JavaScript &mdash; A. Sharif</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://jrsinclair.com/articles/2016/gentle-introduction-to-functional-javascript-functions/\">A Gentle Introduction to Functional JavaScript pt III: Functions for making functions &mdash; James Sinclair</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://jsleao.wordpress.com/2015/02/22/curry-and-compose-why-you-should-be-using-something-like-ramda-in-your-code/\">Curry And Compose (why you should be using something like ramda in your code) &mdash; jsanchesleao</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://vanslaars.io/post/create-pipe-function/\">Function Composition in JavaScript with Pipe &mdash; Andy Van Slaars</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://developer.telerik.com/featured/practical-functional-javascript-ramda/\">Practical Functional JavaScript with Ramda &mdash; Andrew D&#39;Amelio, Yuri Takhteyev</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://hackernoon.com/the-beauty-in-partial-application-currying-and-function-composition-d885bdf0d574\">The beauty in Partial Application, Currying, and Function Composition &mdash; Joel Thoms</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://medium.com/javascript-scene/curry-or-partial-application-8150044c78b8\">Curry or Partial Application? &mdash; Eric Elliott</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://benalman.com/news/2012/09/partial-application-in-javascript/\">Partial Application in JavaScript &mdash; Ben Alman</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://hackernoon.com/partial-application-of-functions-dbe7d9b80760\">Partial Application of Functions &mdash; Functional Reactive Ninja</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://codeburst.io/javascript-currying-vs-partial-application-4db5b2442be8\">Currying vs Partial Application &mdash; Deepak Gupta</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://raganwald.com/2015/04/01/partial-application.html\">Partial Application in ECMAScript 2015 &mdash; Ragan Wald</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://joecortopassi.com/articles/functional-composition-in-javascript/\">Functional Composition in Javascript &mdash; Joe Cortopassi</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://medium.com/%40cscalfani/so-you-want-to-be-a-functional-programmer-part-1-1f15e387e536\">So You Want to be a Functional Programmer pt. I &mdash; Charles Scalfani</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://medium.com/%40cscalfani/so-you-want-to-be-a-functional-programmer-part-2-7005682cec4a\">So You Want to be a Functional Programmer pt. II &mdash; Charles Scalfani</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://medium.com/%40cscalfani/so-you-want-to-be-a-functional-programmer-part-3-1b0fd14eb1a7\">So You Want to be a Functional Programmer pt. III &mdash; Charles Scalfani</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://medium.com/%40cscalfani/so-you-want-to-be-a-functional-programmer-part-4-18fbe3ea9e49\">So You Want to be a Functional Programmer pt. IV &mdash; Charles Scalfani</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://medium.com/%40cscalfani/so-you-want-to-be-a-functional-programmer-part-5-c70adc9cf56a\">So You Want to be a Functional Programmer pt. V &mdash; Charles Scalfani</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/getify/Functional-Light-JS/blob/master/manuscript/ch3.md\">Functional-Light JavaScript Chapter 3: Managing Function Inputs &mdash; Kyle Simpson</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Videos</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v%3DWl2ejJOqHUU\">Compose vs Pipe: Functional Programming in JavaScript &mdash; Chyld Studios</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v%3DjigHxo9YR30\">JavaScript Functional Programing: Compose &mdash; Theodore Anderson</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v%3Dmth5WpEc4Qs\">Function Composition - Functional JavaScript &mdash; NWCalvank</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v%3DUam37AlzPYw\">JavaScript Function Composition Explained &mdash; Theodore Anderson</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v%3DVGB9HbL1GHk\">Let&#39;s code with function composition &mdash; Fun Fun Function</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v%3DDzLkRsUN2vE\">Partial Application vs. Currying &mdash; NWCalvank</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v%3DjkebgHEcvac\">JavaScript Partial Application &mdash; Theodore Anderson</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>33. Clean Code</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>B&agrave;i vit</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/ryanmcdermott/clean-code-javascript\">Clean Code concepts adapted for JavaScript &mdash; Ryan McDermott</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blog.risingstack.com/javascript-clean-coding-best-practices-node-js-at-scale/\">JavaScript Clean Coding Best Practices &mdash; Andr&aacute;s T&oacute;th</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://medium.com/%40kevin_peters/function-parameters-in-javascript-clean-code-4caac109159b\">Function parameters in JavaScript Clean Code &mdash; Kevin Peters</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://css-tricks.com/clean-code-javascript/\">Clean Code JavaScript &mdash; Sarah Drasner</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://codeburst.io/keeping-your-code-clean-d30bcffd1a10\">Keeping your code clean &mdash; Samuel James</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.sitepoint.com/modern-javascript-best-practices/\">Best Practices for Using Modern JavaScript Syntax &mdash; M. David Green</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Videos</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v%3DMus_vwhTCq0\">JavaScript Pro Tips - Code This, NOT That</a></li>\r\n</ul>', '33 khi nim m bt c JavaScript Developer nn bit', '33 khi nim m bt c JavaScript Developer nn bit', '33 khi nim m bt c JavaScript Developer nn bit', '/photos/1/Test/post-default.jpg', 1, 9, 1, '2018-11-12 20:06:28', '2018-11-12 20:06:28');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `name`, `alias`, `category_id`, `posttype_id`, `intro`, `content`, `title`, `keyword`, `description`, `image`, `status`, `view`, `user_id`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(6, 'Hy s dng .gitignore global', 'hay-su-dung-gitignore-global', 3, 1, 'Hy s dng .gitignore global', '<p>Nu bn l&agrave; Developer v&agrave; ang s&nbsp;<strong>git</strong>&nbsp;cho mi d &aacute;n ca m&igrave;nh th&igrave; c&oacute; l c&aacute;c bn s nhn ra mt iu l&agrave; khi to mt d &aacute;n mi c&aacute;c bn s phi khai b&aacute;o c&aacute;c file/folder kh&ocirc;ng cn upload l&ecirc;n serve trong file .gitignore.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nu c&aacute;c file &amp; folder n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng nm trong project ca bn m&agrave; t ng sinh t m&aacute;y ca bn hay phn mm bn ang d&ugrave;ng, v&iacute; d bn x&agrave;i MacOS th&igrave; hay c&oacute; file&nbsp;.DS_STORE, Thumbs.db, ... sinh ra, nu bn code bng&nbsp;PhpStorm hn l&agrave; s c&oacute; th mc .idea trong project ca bn, th&igrave; l&uacute;c n&agrave;y m&igrave;nh ngh bn n&ecirc;n d&ugrave;ng&nbsp;<strong>.gitignore global</strong>&nbsp;c ri &oacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lu &yacute; ch&uacute;t l&agrave; c&aacute;i n&agrave;y ch th&iacute;ch hp khi l&agrave;m 1 m&igrave;nh, project c&aacute; nh&acirc;n. L&agrave;m nh&oacute;m th&igrave; c&aacute;c bn n&ecirc;n copy .gitignore t global v&agrave;o trong project nh&eacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> s dng .gitignore global bn cn m terminal l&ecirc;n v&agrave; g&otilde; lnh sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>D&agrave;nh cho macOS, linux, windows d&ugrave;ng git bash</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>git config --global core.excludesfile &#39;~/.gitignore&#39;</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>D&agrave;nh cho windows d&ugrave;ng cmd, powershell</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>git config --global core.excludesfile &quot;%USERPROFILE%\\.gitignore&quot;</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>v&agrave; sa file .gitignore va sinh ra (tr&ecirc;n windows file n&agrave;y th&ocirc;ng thng s nm &nbsp;C:/users/{myusername}/.gitignore nh&eacute;) v&agrave; lu li hn l&agrave; bn s kh&ocirc;ng phin cho c&aacute;c d &aacute;n sau n&agrave;y. Nu bn c&ograve;n bn khon cha bit cu h&igrave;nh nh th n&agrave;o sao bn kh&ocirc;ng th tham kho file .gitignore di &acirc;y</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code># Mac OS X hidden files\r\n.DS_Store\r\n.DS_Store?\r\n._*\r\n.Spotlight-V100\r\n.Trashes\r\nehthumbs.db\r\nThumbs.db\r\n\r\n# Vim swap files\r\n.*.sw?\r\n\r\n# PhpStorm\r\n.idea\r\n\r\n# vs code\r\n.vscode\r\n\r\n# Sublime Text\r\n*.sublime-project\r\n\r\n# Node\r\nnode_modules\r\nnpm-debug.log\r\nyarn-error.log\r\n.phpunit-watcher-cache.php</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>From:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://murze.be/create-a-global-gitignore\" target=\"_blank\">murze.be</a></p>', 'Hy s dng .gitignore global Ho Minh Blog', 'Hy s dng .gitignore global Ho Minh Blog', 'Hy s dng .gitignore global Ho Minh Blog', '/photos/1/Test/post-default.jpg', 1, 23, 1, '2018-11-12 20:11:54', '2018-11-12 20:11:54'),
(7, 'PHP 7.3 c g mi?', 'php-73-co-gi-moi?', 6, 1, 'is_countable - Kim tra bin c m c hay khng', '<h2><a href=\"https://wiki.php.net/rfc/is-countable\" target=\"_blank\">is_countable - Kim tra bin c&oacute; m c hay kh&ocirc;ng</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>C&oacute; th bn cha bit &oacute; l&agrave;  phi&ecirc;n bn&nbsp;<strong>PHP 7.2</strong>, nu bn d&ugrave;ng h&agrave;m&nbsp;<code>count</code>&nbsp;cho mt bin kh&ocirc;ng m c bn s n WARNING ch&agrave; b&aacute; la ngay:</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>$website = &#39;https://chungnguyen.xyz&#39;;\r\ncount($website);</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>Warning:  count(): Parameter must be an array or an object that implements Countable in ...</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vy cho n&ecirc;n, phi&ecirc;n bn&nbsp;<strong>PHP 7.3</strong>&nbsp;&atilde; cho ra mt h&agrave;m&nbsp;<code>is_countable</code>&nbsp;(Kim tra bin c&oacute; m c hay kh&ocirc;ng) gi&uacute;p cho bn d d&agrave;ng kim tra v&agrave; tr&aacute;nh b n warning</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>$website = &#39;https://chungnguyen.xyz&#39;;\r\n$count = is_countable($website) ? count($website) : null;</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://wiki.php.net/rfc/array_key_first_last\" target=\"_blank\">array_key_first v&agrave; array_key_last</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>n gin l&agrave; 2 h&agrave;m n&agrave;y s tr v gi&aacute; tr ca key u tin v&agrave; key cui c&ugrave;ng trong mng</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>$array = [\r\n    &#39;name&#39; =&gt; &#39;Chung Nguyn&#39;,\r\n    &#39;website&#39; =&gt; &#39;https://chungnguyen.xyz&#39;,\r\n    &#39;length&#39; =&gt; &#39;16cm&#39;,\r\n];\r\narray_key_first($array); // &#39;name&#39;\r\narray_key_last($array); // &#39;length&#39;</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p><code>array_value_first</code>&nbsp;v&agrave;&nbsp;<code>array_value_last</code>&nbsp;cng c  ngh th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o, nhng b ph quyt c&oacute; l ch cn c&oacute; key ca array ri th&igrave; s d d&agrave;ng ly c value n&ecirc;n  ngh kh&ocirc;ng c t&aacute;n th&agrave;nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://wiki.php.net/rfc/flexible_heredoc_nowdoc_syntaxes\" target=\"_blank\">Linh hot trong c&uacute; ph&aacute;p&nbsp;Heredoc v&agrave; Nowdoc</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Nu c qua thy Heredoc, Nowdoc m&agrave; c&aacute;c bn cha h&igrave;nh dung ra n&oacute; l&agrave; g&igrave; th&igrave; m&igrave;nh &ocirc;n li ch&uacute;t x&iacute;u bng v&iacute; d ca Heredoc nh&eacute;</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>// V&iacute; d v Heredoc\r\n$congi = &#39;m&egrave;o&#39;;\r\n$caygi = &#39;cau&#39;;\r\n\r\n$str = &lt;&lt;&lt;CONMEO\r\nCon $congi m&agrave; tr&egrave;o c&acirc;y $caygi,\r\nHi thm ch&uacute; chut i &acirc;u vng nh&agrave;. \r\nCh&uacute; chut i ch ng xa.\r\nMua mm mua mui gi cha ch&uacute; $congi.\r\nCONMEO;\r\n// Kt qu ca echo $str; l&agrave;:\r\n// Con m&egrave;o m&agrave; tr&egrave;o c&acirc;y cau,\r\n// Hi thm ch&uacute; chut i &acirc;u vng nh&agrave;. \r\n// Ch&uacute; chut i ch ng xa.\r\n// Mua mm mua mui gi cha ch&uacute; m&egrave;o.\r\n\r\n// V&iacute; d v Nowdoc\r\n$str = &lt;&lt;&lt;&#39;CONMEO&#39;\r\nCon $congi m&agrave; tr&egrave;o c&acirc;y $caygi,\r\nHi thm ch&uacute; chut i &acirc;u vng nh&agrave;. \r\nCh&uacute; chut i ch ng xa.\r\nMua mm mua mui gi cha ch&uacute; $congi.\r\nCONMEO;\r\n// Kt qu ca echo $str; l&agrave;:\r\n// Con $congi m&agrave; tr&egrave;o c&acirc;y $caygi,\r\n// Hi thm ch&uacute; chut i &acirc;u vng nh&agrave;. \r\n// Ch&uacute; chut i ch ng xa.\r\n// Mua mm mua mui gi cha ch&uacute; $congi.</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>N&oacute; bt u bng &lt;&lt;&lt; tip theo sau &oacute; l&agrave; open tag nh HTML vy v&agrave; cui c&ugrave;ng l&agrave; close tag&nbsp;(c open v&agrave; close tag bt buc xung d&ograve;ng nh&eacute;). Nowdoc cng tng t nh Heredoc nhng n&oacute; s kh&ocirc;ng thay th&nbsp;<code>$congi</code>&nbsp;bng&nbsp;<code>m&egrave;o</code>&nbsp;v&agrave;&nbsp;<code>$caygi</code>&nbsp;bng&nbsp;<code>cau</code>&nbsp;tc l&agrave; c&oacute; g&igrave; in ra ny.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> phi&ecirc;n bn trc close tag CONMEO kia bt buc phi nm d&iacute; s&aacute;t v&agrave;o l vn bn  ch cn nh&iacute;ch mt ch&uacute;t th&ocirc;i l&agrave; bn n c ti nh di ngay</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>Parse error:  syntax error, unexpected end of file in ... on line ...</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ch&iacute;nh s linh hot n&agrave;y cng ny sinh mt vn  nh &oacute; l&agrave; c&oacute; th mt s Heredoc bn nh ngha s b &#39;break&#39;</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>$congi = &#39;m&egrave;o&#39;;\r\n$caygi = &#39;cau&#39;;\r\n\r\n$str = &lt;&lt;&lt;CONMEO\r\nCon $congi m&agrave; tr&egrave;o c&acirc;y $caygi,\r\nHi thm ch&uacute; chut i &acirc;u vng nh&agrave;. \r\nCh&uacute; chut i ch ng xa.\r\nMua mm mua mui gi cha ch&uacute; $congi.\r\n    CONMEO\r\nCONMEO;</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lu &yacute; l&agrave;: close tag  v&iacute; d tr&ecirc;n l&agrave; CONMEO y, n&oacute; m&agrave; d&oacute;ng h&agrave;ng bao nhi&ecirc;u th&igrave; ni dung  b&ecirc;n trong s b tr i tng ng, v&iacute; d cho d hiu nh&eacute;</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>$congi = &#39;m&egrave;o&#39;;\r\n$caygi = &#39;cau&#39;;\r\n\r\n$str = &lt;&lt;&lt;CONMEO\r\n    Con $congi m&agrave; tr&egrave;o c&acirc;y $caygi, &lt;-- b tr i 4 khong trng\r\n        Hi thm ch&uacute; chut i &acirc;u vng nh&agrave;. &lt;-- b tr i 4 khong trng\r\n            Ch&uacute; chut i ch ng xa. &lt;-- b tr i 4 khong trng\r\n                Mua mm mua mui gi cha ch&uacute; $congi. &lt;-- b tr i 4 khong trng\r\n    CONMEO; &lt;-- c&oacute; 4 khong trng\r\n\r\n// kt qu l&agrave;:\r\n\r\n// Con m&egrave;o m&agrave; tr&egrave;o c&acirc;y cau,\r\n//     Hi thm ch&uacute; chut i &acirc;u vng nh&agrave;. \r\n//         Ch&uacute; chut i ch ng xa.\r\n//             Mua mm mua mui gi cha ch&uacute; m&egrave;o.\r\n\r\n// ch kh&ocirc;ng phi ntn &acirc;u nh&eacute;\r\n\r\n//    Con m&egrave;o m&agrave; tr&egrave;o c&acirc;y cau,\r\n//        Hi thm ch&uacute; chut i &acirc;u vng nh&agrave;. \r\n//            Ch&uacute; chut i ch ng xa.\r\n//                Mua mm mua mui gi cha ch&uacute; m&egrave;o.</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://wiki.php.net/rfc/trailing-comma-function-calls\" target=\"_blank\">C&oacute; th th&ecirc;m du phy cui c&ugrave;ng khi gi function</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Vic cho ph&eacute;p th&ecirc;m du phy sau lnh gi h&agrave;m l&agrave;m cho vic b sung tham s trong nhiu ng cnh tr n&ecirc;n thun ti&ecirc;n hn, khi bn gi h&agrave;m c&oacute; nhiu i s, c bit l&agrave; c&aacute;c&nbsp;<code>variadic functions</code>&nbsp;(h&agrave;m c&oacute; tham s kh&ocirc;ng x&aacute;c nh, bao nhi&ecirc;u cng nut).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>T phi&ecirc;n bn PHP 7.2 , vic th&ecirc;m du phy &atilde; c s dng trong c&uacute; ph&aacute;p khai b&aacute;o mng, cng nhng c&uacute; ph&aacute;p&nbsp;<code>namespace</code>&nbsp;.</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code># PHP 7.2\r\nuse Foo\\Bar\\{\r\n    Foo,\r\n    Bar,\r\n};\r\n \r\n$foo = [\r\n    &#39;foo&#39;,\r\n    &#39;bar&#39;,\r\n];</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Du phy cui c&ugrave;ng khi gi function l&agrave;m cho n&oacute; tr n&ecirc;n i&ecirc;n r khi gi bt k h&agrave;m&nbsp;n&agrave;o thuc dng nhiu tham s nh  tr&ecirc;n (<code>variadic functions</code>)</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>// unset t&egrave; le ht me\r\nunset(\r\n    $somethingIDontNeedAnymore,\r\n    $anotherOneToKill,\r\n    $letsMakeThisEasy,\r\n);\r\n\r\n// compact te le ht &eacute;\r\nreturn view(\r\n    &#39;welcome&#39;,\r\n    compact(\r\n        &#39;title&#39;,\r\n        &#39;body&#39;,\r\n        &#39;comments&#39;,\r\n    )\r\n);\r\n\r\n// array_merge te le h&agrave;n the\r\n$newArray = array_merge(\r\n    $arrayOne,\r\n    $arrayTwo,\r\n    [&#39;foo&#39;, &#39;bar&#39;],\r\n);\r\n\r\n// var_dump te le ni ch&egrave;\r\nvar_dump(\r\n    $whatIsInThere,\r\n    $probablyABugInThisOne,\r\n    $oneMoreToCheck,\r\n);</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Method ca class v&agrave; Closure cn bn vn l&agrave; h&agrave;m n&ecirc;n cng tng t.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>B&aacute;o c&aacute;o li tt hn, c th l&agrave; type error</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><code>TypeErrors&nbsp;</code>cho s nguy&ecirc;n v&agrave; booleans c s dng  in ra t&ecirc;n y , n&oacute; &atilde; c i th&agrave;nh&nbsp;<code>int&nbsp;</code>v&agrave;&nbsp;<code>bool</code>,  khp vi type hints  trong code.</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>Argument 1 passed to foo() must be of the type int/bool</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So vi PHP 7.2:</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>Argument 1 passed to foo() must be of the type \r\ninteger/boolean</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://wiki.php.net/rfc/json_throw_on_error\" target=\"_blank\">C&oacute; th throw JSON errors</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>PHP hin c&oacute; 2 h&agrave;m  x l&yacute; JSON l&agrave;&nbsp;<code>json_decode()</code>&nbsp;v&agrave;&nbsp;<code>json_encode()</code>. Tht kh&ocirc;ng may, c hai u kh&ocirc;ng x l&yacute; ti u c c&aacute;c li.&nbsp;<code>json_decode()</code>&nbsp;tr v&nbsp;<code>null</code>&nbsp;khi li, nhng&nbsp;<code>null</code>&nbsp;cng c&oacute; th l&agrave; mt kt qu hp l khi bn decode mt JSON &quot;null&quot;. C&aacute;ch duy nht  bit khi n&agrave;o c&oacute; li xy ra bng c&aacute;ch gi&nbsp;<code>json_last_error()</code>&nbsp;hoc&nbsp;<code>json_last_erro_msg</code>. Nhng m&agrave; 2 h&agrave;m n&agrave;y n&oacute; kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; ngn chn chng tr&igrave;nh thc thi th mi cay ch </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong phi&ecirc;n bn&nbsp;<strong>PHP 7.3</strong>, mt t&iacute;nh nng mi c  xut thay th l&agrave; b sung mt gi&aacute; tr flag mi cho&nbsp;<code>json_decode()</code>&nbsp;v&agrave;&nbsp;<code>json_encode()</code>&nbsp;l&agrave;&nbsp;<code>JSON_THROW_ON_ERROR</code>, khi b li s throw mt&nbsp;<code>JsonException</code>&nbsp;class l&agrave; class con ca&nbsp;<code>Exception</code></p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>try {\r\n    json_encode($data, JSON_THROW_ON_ERROR);\r\n    json_decode(&quot;invalid json&quot;, null, 512, JSON_THROW_ON_ERROR);\r\n} catch (\\JsonException $e) {\r\n    // code\r\n}</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://wiki.php.net/rfc/list_reference_assignment\" target=\"_blank\"><code>list</code>&nbsp;reference assignment</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Hin ti PHP ch c&oacute; th s dng c&aacute;c&nbsp;reference assignement&nbsp;vi&nbsp;<code>list()</code>.&nbsp;RFC&nbsp; xut c&uacute; ph&aacute;p  cover n&oacute; nh sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>$array = [1, 2];\r\nlist($a, &amp;$b) = $array;</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>N&oacute; cng tng ng vi:</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>$array = [1, 2];\r\n$a = $array[0];\r\n$b =&amp; $array[1];\r\n\r\n/* Note; c&uacute; ph&aacute;p []=  cng hot ng tng t */\r\n[$a, &amp;$b] = $array;</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tt nhi&ecirc;n, iu &oacute; hot ng ging nh&nbsp;<code>list()</code>&nbsp; phi&ecirc;n bn trc, bn vn c&oacute; th s dng&nbsp;<code>list()</code>&nbsp;lng nhau</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>$array = [1, 2, 3, [3, 4]];\r\nlist(&amp;$a, $b,, list(&amp;$c, $d)) = $array;\r\nvar_dump($array);\r\n\r\n/*\r\narray(4) {\r\n  [0]=&gt;\r\n  &amp;int(1)\r\n  [1]=&gt;\r\n  int(2)\r\n  [2]=&gt;\r\n  int(3)\r\n  [3]=&gt;\r\n  array(2) {\r\n    [0]=&gt;\r\n    &amp;int(3)\r\n    [1]=&gt;\r\n    int(4)\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n*/\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hot ng b&igrave;nh thng vi&nbsp;foreach()</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>$array = [[1, 2], [3, 4]];\r\nforeach ($array as list(&amp;$a, $b)) {\r\n    $a = 7;\r\n}\r\nvar_dump($array);/*\r\narray(2) {\r\n  [0]=&gt;\r\n  array(2) {\r\n    [0]=&gt;\r\n    int(7)\r\n    [1]=&gt;\r\n    int(2)\r\n  }\r\n  [1]=&gt;\r\n  array(2) {\r\n    [0]=&gt;\r\n    &amp;int(7)\r\n    [1]=&gt;\r\n    int(4)\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n*/</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://wiki.php.net/rfc/compact\" target=\"_blank\">Bin kh&ocirc;ng x&aacute;c nh trong compact</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Nu bn np v&agrave;o h&agrave;m&nbsp;<code>compact()</code>&nbsp;mt bin kh&ocirc;ng x&aacute;c nh, bn s nhn c ngay mt notice ngon l&agrave;nh c&agrave;nh &agrave;o ngay</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>$a = &#39;foo&#39;;\r\n\r\ncompact(&#39;a&#39;, &#39;b&#39;); \r\n\r\n// Notice: compact(): Undefined variable: b</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://wiki.php.net/rfc/case_insensitive_constant_deprecation\" target=\"_blank\">Phn i v&agrave; loi b Case-insensitive constant</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Nu bn nh ngha hng s bng h&agrave;m&nbsp;<code>define()</code>&nbsp;bn s thy tham s th 3&nbsp;$case_insensitive (trng hp s &yacute;) mc nh l&agrave; false, nu bn code nh th n&agrave;y:</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>define(&#39;CONSTANT&#39;, &#39;Hello world.&#39;, true);\r\n\r\n// kh&ocirc;ng ph&acirc;n bit hoa thng\r\necho CONSTANT; // kt qu l&agrave;: Hello world.\r\necho constant; // kt qu l&agrave;: Hello world.\r\necho Constant; // kt qu l&agrave;: Hello world.</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Phi&ecirc;n bn&nbsp;<strong>PHP 7.3</strong>&nbsp;s loi b tham s th 3 n&agrave;y! C&aacute;c bn lu &yacute; khi n&acirc;ng cp PHP version nh&eacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://wiki.php.net/rfc/same-site-cookie\" target=\"_blank\">Same site cookie</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Thay i n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng ch th&ecirc;m mt tham s mi, n&oacute; cng thay i c&aacute;ch c&aacute;c h&agrave;m&nbsp;<code>setcookie</code>,&nbsp;<code>setrawcookie</code>&nbsp;v&agrave;&nbsp;<code>session_set_cookie_params</code>&nbsp;hot ng theo c&aacute;ch kh&ocirc;ng ph&aacute; v ch&uacute;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>RFC &atilde; b phiu t&aacute;n th&agrave;nh trng hp th 2 &oacute; l&agrave; thay v&igrave; th&ecirc;m mt tham s na v&agrave;o c&aacute;c h&agrave;m &atilde; c&oacute; sn, gi &acirc;y ch&uacute;ng h tr mt lot c&aacute;c t&ugrave;y chn, trong khi vn c&ograve;n tng th&iacute;ch ngc. V&iacute; d:</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>bool setcookie(\r\n    string $name \r\n    [, string $value = &quot;&quot; \r\n    [, int $expire = 0 \r\n    [, string $path = &quot;&quot; \r\n    [, string $domain = &quot;&quot; \r\n    [, bool $secure = false \r\n    [, bool $httponly = false ]]]]]] \r\n)\r\n\r\nbool setcookie ( \r\n    string $name \r\n    [, string $value = &quot;&quot; \r\n    [, int $expire = 0 \r\n    [, array $options ]]] \r\n)\r\n\r\n// C 2 u hot ng. Set Same Site Cookie  trng hp 2</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vic b sung Same Site Cookie c&oacute; &yacute; ngha rt ln trong vic&nbsp;<a href=\"https://security.stackexchange.com/questions/121971/will-same-site-cookies-be-sufficent-protection-against-csrf-and-xss\" target=\"_blank\">ph&ograve;ng chng attack&nbsp;CSRF, XSS v&agrave; XSSI</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://wiki.php.net/rfc/deprecations_php_7_3\" target=\"_blank\">Kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n chp nhn  PHP 7.3</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Mt s iu nh s kh&ocirc;ng c chp nhn  phi&ecirc;n bn PHP 7.3 n&agrave;y, mt li kh nng xy ra trong code ca bn v&igrave; iu n&agrave;y.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>B khi document mbstring function aliases</li>\r\n	<li>C&aacute;c h&agrave;m t&igrave;m kim String (<code>strpos</code>,&nbsp;<code>strrpos</code>,&nbsp;<code>stripos</code>,&nbsp;<code>strripos</code>,&nbsp;<code>strstr</code>,&nbsp;<code>strchr</code>,&nbsp;<code>strrchr</code>&nbsp;v&agrave;&nbsp;<code>stristr</code>)&nbsp; tham s th 2 ($needle) th&ocirc;ng thng l&agrave; string, nhng nu np v&agrave;o kh&ocirc;ng phi string n&oacute; s convert th&agrave;nh s v&agrave; c hiu nh&nbsp;ASCII.  PHP 7.3 n&oacute; s n&eacute;m ra mt cnh b&aacute;o, vy n&ecirc;n bn h&atilde;y c gng np v&agrave;o mt string  tham s th 2 nh&eacute;, PHP 8 s kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n cnh b&aacute;o m&agrave; n&oacute; s convert needle th&agrave;nh string.</li>\r\n	<li><code>fgetss()</code>&nbsp;function v&agrave; string.strip_tags filter s dng s n cnh b&aacute;o, PHP 8 b lu&ocirc;n.</li>\r\n	<li><code>assert()</code>&nbsp;function: compile s b&aacute;o warning v&agrave; PHP 8 compile s b&aacute;o error</li>\r\n	<li><code>FILTER_FLAG_SCHEME_REQUIRED</code>&nbsp;v&agrave;&nbsp;<code>FILTER_FLAG_HOST_REQUIRED</code>&nbsp;flags</li>\r\n	<li><code>pdo_odbc.db2_instance_name</code>&nbsp;php.ini directive:&nbsp;Th&ecirc;m th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o kh&ocirc;ng d&ugrave;ng na nu trong&nbsp;<code>php.ini</code>&nbsp;directive c&oacute; gi&aacute; tr pdo_odbc.db2_instance_name khi khi to module.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'PHP 7.3 c g mi? - Ho Minh Blog', 'PHP 7.3 c g mi? - Ho Minh Blog', 'PHP 7.3 c g mi? - Ho Minh Blog', '/photos/1/php-7-3-co-gi-moi-medium.jpg', 1, 22, 1, '2018-11-14 00:28:06', '2018-11-14 00:28:06'),
(8, 'Laravel Security: n thng tin quan trng trong file .env bt debug mode', 'laravel-security:-an-thong-tin-quan-trong-trong-file-env-bat-debug-mode', 3, 1, 'File .env c th ni l file quan trng bt nht trong b source code Laravel ca bn c phi khng no? Ni y n cha hng t cc thng tin nhy cm khc nhau nh l: APP_KEY, DB_USERNAME, DB_PASSWORD, token ca cc bn th 3', '<p>File&nbsp;<code>.env</code>&nbsp;c&oacute; th n&oacute;i l&agrave;&nbsp;<strong>file quan trng bt nht</strong>&nbsp;trong b source code&nbsp;<a href=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/go/5bgvy7\">Laravel</a>&nbsp;ca bn c&oacute; phi kh&ocirc;ng n&agrave;o? Ni &acirc;y n&oacute; cha h&aacute;ng t&aacute; c&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng tin nhy cm kh&aacute;c nhau nh l&agrave;:&nbsp;<code>APP_KEY</code>,&nbsp;<code>DB_USERNAME</code>,&nbsp;<code>DB_PASSWORD</code>, token ca c&aacute;c b&ecirc;n th 3, ...&nbsp;&oacute; ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; l&iacute; do m&agrave; Root Document ca Laravel phi tr v&agrave;o th mc&nbsp;<code>public</code>, tr&aacute;nh truy cp ngc v&agrave;o source v&agrave; c bit l&agrave; file&nbsp;<code>.env</code>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>N&oacute;i n &acirc;y th&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; g&igrave; phi b&agrave;n phi kh&ocirc;ng n&agrave;o, nhng cuc sng m&agrave;&nbsp; thnh thong c&oacute;&nbsp;nhng ngi kh&aacute;c ang xem x&eacute;t c&ocirc;ng vic ph&aacute;t trin ca bn v&agrave; bn kh&ocirc;ng mun h nh&igrave;n thy nhng th&ocirc;ng tin nhy cm n&agrave;y nu ng dng ang chy b li , nhng bn cng kh&ocirc;ng mun phi tip tc bt hay tt g li&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel/laravel-security-an-thong-tin-quan-trong-trong-file-env-bat-debug-mode-1.png\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\nHoc c&oacute; &ocirc;i khi ng dng ca bn  tr&ecirc;n production, ph&aacute;t sinh mt li bn kh&ocirc;ng t&agrave;i n&agrave;o bit c n&oacute; l&agrave; g&igrave;, bn ch mun th bt debug l&ecirc;n trong t&iacute;ch tt  coi n&oacute; l&agrave; g&igrave; ri tt nhng li s b ngi d&ugrave;ng v&ocirc; t&igrave;nh bt gp v&agrave; thy c. Vy th&igrave; gii ph&aacute;p di &acirc;y d&agrave;nh cho bn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>H&atilde;y m file&nbsp;<code>config/app.php</code>&nbsp;bn kim tra xem c&oacute; key n&agrave;o t&ecirc;n l&agrave; &#39;<code>debug_blacklist</code>&#39; hay kh&ocirc;ng, nu kh&ocirc;ng bn h&atilde;y to mt key nh vy v&agrave; in ni dung n&agrave;y v&agrave;o</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>return [\r\n\r\n    // ...\r\n\r\n    &#39;debug_blacklist&#39; =&gt; [\r\n        &#39;_ENV&#39; =&gt; [\r\n            &#39;APP_KEY&#39;,\r\n            &#39;DB_PASSWORD&#39;,\r\n            &#39;REDIS_PASSWORD&#39;,\r\n            &#39;MAIL_PASSWORD&#39;,\r\n            &#39;PUSHER_APP_KEY&#39;,\r\n            &#39;PUSHER_APP_SECRET&#39;,\r\n            // th&ecirc;m key bn cho rng nhy cm v&agrave;o &acirc;y\r\n        ],\r\n        &#39;_SERVER&#39; =&gt; [\r\n            &#39;APP_KEY&#39;,\r\n            &#39;DB_PASSWORD&#39;,\r\n            &#39;REDIS_PASSWORD&#39;,\r\n            &#39;MAIL_PASSWORD&#39;,\r\n            &#39;PUSHER_APP_KEY&#39;,\r\n            &#39;PUSHER_APP_SECRET&#39;,\r\n            // v&agrave;o &acirc;y\r\n        ],\r\n        &#39;_POST&#39; =&gt; [\r\n            &#39;password&#39;,\r\n            // v&agrave; v&agrave;o &acirc;y na\r\n        ],\r\n    ],\r\n];</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel/laravel-security-an-thong-tin-quan-trong-trong-file-env-bat-debug-mode-2.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>n th&ocirc;ng tin nhy cm trong file .env khi whoops</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nu bn mun n tt c  =)) c th&ocirc;i, c&aacute;ch di &acirc;y s ch cho bn l&agrave;m iu &oacute; m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; ch&uacute;t kh&oacute; khn n&agrave;o&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>&lt;?php\r\n\r\nreturn [\r\n\r\n    // ...\r\n\r\n    &#39;debug_blacklist&#39; =&gt; [\r\n        &#39;_COOKIE&#39; =&gt; array_keys($_COOKIE),\r\n        &#39;_SERVER&#39; =&gt; array_keys($_SERVER),\r\n        &#39;_ENV&#39; =&gt; array_keys($_ENV),        \r\n    ],\r\n];</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel/laravel-security-an-thong-tin-quan-trong-trong-file-env-bat-debug-mode-3.png\" /></p>', 'Laravel Security: n thng tin quan trng trong file .env bt debug mode - Ho Minh Blog', 'Laravel Security: n thng tin quan trng trong file .env bt debug mode - Ho Minh Blog', 'Laravel Security: n thng tin quan trng trong file .env bt debug mode - Ho Minh Blog', '/photos/1/laravel-security-an-thong-tin-quan-trong-trong-file-env-bat-debug-mode-medium.jpg', 1, 26, 1, '2018-11-14 18:43:25', '2018-11-14 18:43:25'),
(9, 'Gii thiu v Laravel Telescope - Siu phm ma thu 2018', 'gioi-thieu-ve-laravel-telescope---sieu-pham-mua-thu-2018', 3, 1, 'Laravel Telescope l mt tr l g ri ng dng mi t Laravel, c vit bi Mohamed Said v Taylor Otwell. Laravel Telescope l m ngun m, min ph trn GitHub v s c pht hnh vo tun ti (hin ti l 2018-10-19).', '<p><strong>Laravel Telescope</strong>&nbsp;l&agrave; mt tr l&yacute; g ri ng dng mi t Laravel, c vit bi Mohamed Said v&agrave; Taylor Otwell.&nbsp;<strong>Laravel Telescope</strong>&nbsp;l&agrave; m&atilde; ngun m, min ph&iacute; tr&ecirc;n GitHub v&agrave; s c ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh v&agrave;o tun ti (hin ti l&agrave; 2018-10-19).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel-telescope/telescope-start-page.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>H&igrave;nh nh c chp trc tip ti hi ngh Laracon din ra ti &Uacute;c n&ecirc;n cht lng hi c chui nh&eacute;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bn s b n&oacute; v&agrave;o c&aacute;c ng dng ca bn nh l&agrave; mt depedency ca b&ecirc;n th ba th&ocirc;ng qua&nbsp;<a href=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/go/ykRF39\"><strong>Composer</strong></a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Khi bn c&agrave;i t Telescope, bn s truy cp n&oacute; bng c&aacute;ch truy cp v&agrave;o&nbsp;<code>/telescope</code>&nbsp;ca ng dng ca bn.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Laravel Telescope l&agrave; g&igrave;?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Telescope ting anh ngha l&agrave; K&iacute;nh vin vng, chc l&agrave; mun n&oacute;i l&agrave; n&oacute; c&oacute; th nh&igrave;n c xa t&iacute;t m&ugrave; khi lu&ocirc;n ha</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nu bn &atilde; tng s dng Clockwork hoc Laravel Debugbar, h&atilde;y ngh rng n&oacute; l&agrave; c lp UI v&agrave; c&oacute; si&ecirc;u nng lc i cho n&oacute; ngu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Telescope ging nh bn cnh v bo v a con g&aacute;i nh&agrave; gi&agrave;u, b l&agrave;m to (ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; project ca bn - l&agrave;m m&igrave;nh li&ecirc;n tng n b phim In Time - Thi khc sinh t, nu rnh bn c&oacute; th xem), Telescope s theo d&otilde;i&nbsp;mi y&ecirc;u cu i v&agrave;o ng dng ca bn, cho d&ugrave; t y&ecirc;u cu HTTP, t d&ograve;ng lnh, t tr&igrave;nh l&ecirc;n lch hoc t h&agrave;ng i (Clockwork hoc Laravel Debugbar chc ch  ngi kh&oacute;i). M&igrave;nh tm gi Telescope l&agrave; nhng ngi theo d&otilde;i vy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nhng ngi theo d&otilde;i n&agrave;y nm bt tt c c&aacute;c loi th&ocirc;ng tin v c&aacute;c y&ecirc;u cu hay d liu li&ecirc;n quan - nhng th nh truy vn c s d liu (database queries) v&agrave; thi gian thc hin (execution time), ln truy cp b nh cache (cache hits) v&agrave; s ln b l (misses), events fired, th c gi v&agrave; nhiu th kh&aacute;c na...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Di &acirc;y l&agrave; lit k&ecirc; s s c&oacute; bao nhi&ecirc;u thng theo d&otilde;i n&egrave;:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Requests</li>\r\n	<li>Commands</li>\r\n	<li>Schedule</li>\r\n	<li>Jobs</li>\r\n	<li>Exceptions</li>\r\n	<li>Logs</li>\r\n	<li>Dumps</li>\r\n	<li>Queries</li>\r\n	<li>Models</li>\r\n	<li>Events</li>\r\n	<li>Mail</li>\r\n	<li>Notifications</li>\r\n	<li>Cache</li>\r\n	<li>Redis</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h2>Tabs/watchers</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>H&atilde;y xem qua tng tab n&agrave;y v&agrave; nhng g&igrave; nh&eacute;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>(HTTP) Requests</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"telescope request\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel-telescope/telescope-requests.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tab n&agrave;y cho ph&eacute;p bn xem tt c c&aacute;c y&ecirc;u cu HTTP i v&agrave;o ng dng ca bn. Bn s c&oacute; th xem x&eacute;t tt c c&aacute;c y&ecirc;u cu HTTP v&agrave; tt c c&aacute;c loi th&ocirc;ng tin hu &iacute;ch v tng y&ecirc;u cu. V&iacute; d:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>payload</li>\r\n	<li>headers</li>\r\n	<li>session</li>\r\n	<li>response</li>\r\n	<li>hostname</li>\r\n	<li>method</li>\r\n	<li>path</li>\r\n	<li>status</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Mi trang y&ecirc;u cu cng hin th bt k d liu n&agrave;o m&agrave; n&oacute; c&oacute; t nhng ngi theo d&otilde;i kh&aacute;c c&oacute; li&ecirc;n quan n y&ecirc;u cu n&agrave;y; v&iacute; d, tt c c&aacute;c truy vn c s d liu v&agrave; ch&uacute;ng mt bao l&acirc;u; ngi d&ugrave;ng n&agrave;o c x&aacute;c thc cho y&ecirc;u cu n&agrave;y; v&agrave; hn th na.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel-telescope/telescope-basic-request-inspection.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Commands &amp; Schedule</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel-telescope/telescope-command-details.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tab commands&nbsp;v&agrave; tab schedule&nbsp;cho ph&eacute;p bn xem danh s&aacute;ch tt c c&aacute;c lnh &atilde; chy v&agrave; exit code ca ch&uacute;ng, xem c&aacute;c i s v&agrave; t&ugrave;y chn ca ch&uacute;ng v&agrave; tr&ecirc;n trang schedule xem tt c th&ocirc;ng tin lp lch ca ch&uacute;ng nh lch biu cron ca ch&uacute;ng (v&iacute; d * * * * *).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel-telescope/telescope-schedule.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Jobs</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel-telescope/telescope-jobs.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tab c&ocirc;ng vic lit k&ecirc; tt c c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng vic &atilde; chy hoc tt c chy.&nbsp;N&oacute; tng t nh Horizon, nhng l&agrave; Redis-only v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng ch l&agrave; giao din ngi d&ugrave;ng - n&oacute; cng tng t&aacute;c vi queue works ang chy. mt kh&aacute;c Telescope, ch l&agrave; mt giao din ngi d&ugrave;ng, nhng n&oacute; cng hot ng cho tt c queue drivers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tr&ecirc;n trang danh s&aacute;ch c&ocirc;ng vic, bn s c&oacute; th thy t&ecirc;n c&ocirc;ng vic, h&agrave;ng i v&agrave; kt ni m&agrave; n&oacute; chy, trng th&aacute;i ca n&oacute; v&agrave; khi n&oacute; xy ra.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tr&ecirc;n trang chi tit c&ocirc;ng vic bn s c&oacute; th xem tt c d liu &oacute; v&agrave; hn th na: t&ecirc;n m&aacute;y ch, t&ecirc;n y  ca job class, kt ni, h&agrave;ng i, s ln th, thi gian ch, tag.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>C&ocirc;ng vic c t ng gn th vi bt k Eloquent model &iacute;nh k&egrave;m n&agrave;o (v&iacute; d:&nbsp;<code>App\\Video:1</code>), vi ngi d&ugrave;ng nu c&oacute; ngi d&ugrave;ng c &iacute;nh k&egrave;m, v.v.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Cng ging nh vi c&aacute;c y&ecirc;u cu HTTP, bn c&oacute; th xem tt c c&aacute;c loi th&ocirc;ng tin li&ecirc;n quan n c&ocirc;ng vic n&agrave;y nh c&aacute;c truy vn c s d liu m&agrave; n&oacute; &atilde; k&iacute;ch hot, c&ocirc;ng vic m&agrave; c&ocirc;ng vic n&agrave;y khi ng v&agrave; mi bn ghi m&agrave; n&oacute; to ra.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>New queued closures.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Taylor &atilde; &oacute;ng g&oacute;p cho mt th vin mi  a tr li queued closures, m&agrave; Laravel &atilde; tng c&oacute; nhng &atilde; bin mt mt thi gian trc &acirc;y. Vi s &oacute;ng g&oacute;p v&agrave; th vin mi n&agrave;y, nu bn&nbsp;<code>use</code>mt model  import n&oacute; v&agrave;o trong closure, n&oacute; s lu tr ID ca model, kh&ocirc;ng phi to&agrave;n b model, iu &oacute; tt hn nhiu (v&agrave; c&aacute;c lp h&agrave;ng i &atilde; l&agrave;m). V&igrave; vy, queue closures &atilde; tr li!</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>dispatch(function () use ($video) {      // l&agrave;m th g&igrave; &oacute; vi queued job  });</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Exceptions</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel-telescope/telescope-exceptions.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ghi li tt c c&aacute;c ngoi l v&agrave; cho ph&eacute;p bn kim tra tng trng hp ngoi l. iu n&agrave;y s hin th cho bn d liu tng t vi c&aacute;c tab kh&aacute;c, nh t&ecirc;n m&aacute;y ch, loi, y&ecirc;u cu, tag, ngi d&ugrave;ng c x&aacute;c thc.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Logs</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel-telescope/telescope-logs.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hin th th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o tng tr&igrave;nh, mc , khi n&agrave;o n&oacute; xy ra, nu truyn v&agrave;o mt mng bn c&oacute; th xem tt c d liu &oacute;, ngo&agrave;i ra c&ograve;n xem request n&agrave;o k&iacute;ch hot log, ngi d&ugrave;ng n&agrave;o &atilde; k&iacute;ch hot. &quot;p v&agrave; d hiu hn trc &acirc;y, vi vic &agrave;o bi trong ng k&yacute; t t&ugrave;m lum t&agrave; la&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Dump screen</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel-telescope/telescope-dump.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;&acirc;y l&agrave; mt trong nhng t&iacute;nh nng y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch ca t&ocirc;i&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nu bn thc hin&nbsp;<code>dump()</code>&nbsp;trong code v&agrave; bn m n&oacute; trong&nbsp;<strong>Telescope</strong>, bn s thy dumps trong&nbsp;<strong>Telescope</strong>&nbsp;ch kh&ocirc;ng phi ng dng thc t ca bn.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Queries</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Danh s&aacute;ch tt c c&aacute;c truy vn DB ca bn - ging g&oacute;i Debugbar. Xem truy vn y , y&ecirc;u cu n&agrave;o &atilde; k&iacute;ch hot truy vn, mt bao l&acirc;u v.v ...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ch  view &atilde; c&nbsp;format rt p.</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>select      *  from      `users`  order by      `name`</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel-telescope/telescope-pretty-query.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Truy vn n&agrave;o g&acirc;y mt nhiu thi gian, n&oacute; s gn mt c&aacute;i th slow  ch&eacute;t cho bn bit m&agrave; sa (h&igrave;nh  di k phi nha)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel-telescope/telescope-queries.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Models</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Bn c&oacute; th xem create, update, delete events; cho thy nhng thay i &atilde; c thc hin, v.v.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel-telescope/telescope-models.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Events</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Hin th danh s&aacute;ch tt c c&aacute;c s kin, bn c&oacute; th xem s kin n&agrave;o c broadcast with a tag; xem danh s&aacute;ch tt c c&aacute;c listeners c to ra</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel-telescope/telescope-events.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Mail</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Hin th danh s&aacute;ch tt c c&aacute;c email &atilde; c gi; ai l&agrave; ngi nhn; khi n&agrave;o n&oacute; xy ra; cho d&ugrave; &oacute; l&agrave; h&agrave;ng i v&agrave; sau khi ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh xong  h&agrave;ng i. C&oacute; th xem email subject v&agrave; khi v&agrave;o s&acirc;u hn cng s thy bn xem trc ca email nh MailTrap vy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel-telescope/telescope-mail-preview.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Notifications</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Hin th tt c th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o, loi ch&uacute;ng l&agrave; g&igrave;, v.v.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Cache</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Hin th lt truy cp b nh cache v&agrave; c&aacute;c ln b l v&agrave; cp nht v.v</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hin th kh&oacute;a, d liu, khi n&agrave;o ht hn, c&oacute; th xem request n&agrave;o k&iacute;ch hot n&oacute; v&agrave; cng tr&ecirc;n trang request, bn c&oacute; th xem tt c c&aacute;c ln truy cp b nh cache/misses</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel-telescope/telescope-cache.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Redis</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Tng t nh cache</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Authenticated user</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Nhn th&ocirc;ng tin v ngi d&ugrave;ng c x&aacute;c thc tr&ecirc;n bt k&nbsp;tab n&agrave;o</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Authorization</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>List danh s&aacute;ch email ai &atilde; access trong telescope service provider</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Filtering</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>T  tr&ecirc;n xung ti di bn thy y, nhiu v&atilde;i phi k n&agrave;o, b lc l&agrave; c&aacute;ch  lc bt, ly c&aacute;i n&agrave;o bn cn th&ocirc;i. Trong Telescope service provider</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>Telescope::filter(function ($entry) {      // local th&igrave; ly ht      if (local) { return true; }        // ly c&aacute;i m&igrave;nh cn th&ocirc;i      return $entry-&gt;isReportableException ||          $entry-&gt;isfailedJob() ||          $entry-&gt;isScheduledTask() ||          $entry-&gt;hasMonitoredTag();  })</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Miscellaneous</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Laravel Telescope c&ograve;n c&oacute; ch  ban &ecirc;m na, kh&ocirc;ng bit b  &acirc;u i kh&aacute;i&nbsp;<code>Telescope::night()</code>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel-telescope/telescope-night-mode.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Hi &aacute;p</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>D liu c lu tr  &acirc;u?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Redis, ngo&agrave;i ra c&oacute; 6-7 c&aacute;ch g&igrave; na cho bn chn &aacute;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Lu tr bao nhi&ecirc;u d liu?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Khong 100 mi ln</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>C&oacute; th nhn c th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o cho Slack kh&ocirc;ng?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>C&oacute;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>C&oacute; th lc theo thi gian kh&ocirc;ng?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>B&acirc;y gi th&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng, nhng n&oacute; l&agrave; open source bn c&oacute; th sa n&oacute;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>T&aacute;c ng ca n&oacute; i vi thi gian khi ng (c&oacute; nh hng tc ) kh&ocirc;ng?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Ch c&oacute; mt truy vn c thc thi mi ln. Thng th&igrave; bn chc kh&ocirc;ng d&ugrave;ng n&oacute; tr&ecirc;n production &acirc;u nh, n&oacute; l&agrave; debug m&agrave;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>c&oacute; th kim tra nhiu ng dng trong mt giao din ngi d&ugrave;ng kh&ocirc;ng?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, ch cn ch cho h ng nhp th&ocirc;ng tin ca h trong c&ugrave;ng mt c s d liu</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngun:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://mattstauffer.com/blog/introducing-laravel-telescope/\">@mattstauffer</a></p>', 'Gii thiu v Laravel Telescope - Siu phm ma thu 2018 - Ho Minh Blog', 'Gii thiu v Laravel Telescope - Siu phm ma thu 2018 - Ho Minh Blog', 'Gii thiu v Laravel Telescope - Siu phm ma thu 2018 - Ho Minh Blog', '/photos/1/gioi-thieu-ve-laravel-telescope-sieu-pham-mua-thu-2018-medium.jpg', 1, 113, 1, '2018-11-14 23:36:34', '2018-11-14 23:36:34');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `name`, `alias`, `category_id`, `posttype_id`, `intro`, `content`, `title`, `keyword`, `description`, `image`, `status`, `view`, `user_id`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(10, 'PHP 7.4: Preload - Tc  bn th cho PHP', 'php-74:-preload---toc-do-ban-tho-cho-php', 6, 1, 'PHP Preload - what the hell, man?', '<p><strong>PHP Preload</strong>&nbsp;- what the hell, man? </p>\r\n\r\n<h2>PHP Lifecycle - PHP opcode</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Trc khi n&oacute;i v&nbsp;<strong>PHP Preload</strong>&nbsp;cho Chung c ph&eacute;p n&oacute;i mt ch&uacute;t v qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh m&agrave; mt file PHP khi chy.&nbsp;Khi ch&uacute;ng ta chy mt on code PHP, c&oacute; rt nhiu th xy ra s&acirc;u b&ecirc;n di m&agrave; ta kh&ocirc;ng nh&igrave;n thy. Mt c&aacute;ch kh&aacute;i qu&aacute;t, b th&ocirc;ng dch PHP tri qua 4 giai on khi n&oacute; thc thi 1 on code (Xem th&ecirc;m v 4 giai on n&agrave;y&nbsp;<a href=\"https://techmaster.vn/posts/34207/php-chay-nhu-nao-tu-source-code-den-render\" target=\"_blank\">ti &acirc;y</a>):</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Lexing</li>\r\n	<li>Parsing</li>\r\n	<li>Bi&ecirc;n dch (compilation)</li>\r\n	<li>Th&ocirc;ng dch (intepretation)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/photos/1/php-life-circle.png\" style=\"height:192px; width:935px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nh&igrave;n v&agrave;o tm h&igrave;nh tr&igrave;nh bn s thy khi mt file PHP c gi  thc thi n&oacute; s tri qua 4 bc u ti&ecirc;n n cui c&ugrave;ng tr v kt qu cho ngi d&ugrave;ng. Qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh n&agrave;y l&agrave; cn thit cho vic thc thi lnh ln u, nhng thc s kh&ocirc;ng cn thit cho nhng ln gi sau &oacute;, v&igrave; qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh vn thc hin y  4 bc trong khi&nbsp;<strong>ch cn bc th 4 (chy opcode) l&agrave; </strong>, d&ugrave; file PHP kh&ocirc;ng h c&oacute; s thay i.&nbsp;iu n&agrave;y ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n ch&iacute;nh dn ti s tr&igrave; tr chm chp ca PHP!!!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>c n &acirc;y, ngi b&igrave;nh thng cng s tht l&ecirc;n: &quot;u xanh rau m&aacute; sao c&oacute; c&aacute;ch n&agrave;o b 3 bc u ti&ecirc;n i cho  kh, m&agrave; c&ograve;n nhanh hn kh&ocirc;ng &quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>----- &Uacute;NG ----</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ch&iacute;nh t &oacute; mi ny sinh mt th gi l&agrave; OPCODE CACHE. Opcode cache ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh cache li 3 bc u ti&ecirc;n, t &acirc;y khi PHP c gi n&oacute; s kim tra xem file php &atilde; c cache opcode hay cha, nu c&oacute; ri n&oacute; s chy lu&ocirc;n opcode m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng cn phi tr qua 3 bc l&atilde;ng ph&iacute; kia.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/photos/1/php-life-circle-after-cache.png\" style=\"height:335px; width:940px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>C&acirc;u chuyn i n &acirc;y coi nh kt th&uacute;c ri nha. Bn n&agrave;o c&ograve;n ln tn opcode l&agrave; g&igrave; th&igrave; n&oacute; vit tt ca t&nbsp;<strong>operation code</strong>, n&oacute; gn tng ng vi file .java sau khi bi&ecirc;n dch l&agrave; .class v&agrave; .dll trong .NET</p>\r\n\r\n<p>n thi im n&agrave;y,&nbsp;<strong>opcode cache</strong>&nbsp;&atilde; tri qua my i t&nbsp;APC&nbsp;&rArr; Turck MMCache&nbsp;&rArr; Zend OpCache mang li cho PHP mt tc  tng i tt v&agrave; d&agrave;nh c s tr&acirc;n trng n b&acirc;y gi.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>PHP Preload l&agrave; g&igrave;? T&igrave;m hiu v PHP Preload</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Nh &atilde; tr&igrave;nh b&agrave;y  tr&ecirc;n,&nbsp;vi b nh cache opcode, c&aacute;c tp c bi&ecirc;n dch mt ln (trong request u ti&ecirc;n), v&agrave; sau &oacute; c lu tr trong b nh d&ugrave;ng chung. Tt c c&aacute;c y&ecirc;u cu HTTP sau &oacute; s c s dng trong b nh chia s.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/photos/1/opcache-gui.png\" style=\"height:918px; width:999px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong khi lu tr c&aacute;c tp tin trong mt b nh cache opcode loi b &atilde; loi b c thi gian ti&ecirc;u tn cho bi&ecirc;n dch -&nbsp;<strong>NHNG</strong>&nbsp;vn c&ograve;n&nbsp;thi gian ti&ecirc;u tn li&ecirc;n quan n vic&nbsp;<strong>ly mt tp tin t b nh cache</strong>&nbsp;.&nbsp;<strong>Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i (PHP)</strong>&nbsp;vn phi&nbsp;<strong>kim tra xem tp tin ngun &atilde; c sa i cha</strong>, sao ch&eacute;p mt s phn nht nh ca class v&agrave; function t b nh m chia s sang b nh process, ... &aacute;ng ch&uacute; &yacute;, v&igrave; mi tp PHP c bi&ecirc;n dch v&agrave; lu tr ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n c lp vi bt k tp n&agrave;o kh&aacute;c, ch&uacute;ng ta&nbsp;<strong>c&oacute; th kh&ocirc;ng gii quyt c</strong>&nbsp;s ph thuc gia c&aacute;c lp c lu tr trong c&aacute;c tp kh&aacute;c nhau khi ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i lu tr c&aacute;c tp trong b nh cache opcode v&agrave; phi li&ecirc;n kt li c&aacute;c ph thuc lp v&agrave;o thi gian chy tr&ecirc;n mi y&ecirc;u cu (request).</p>\r\n\r\n<p> xut ln n&agrave;y (Preload) c ly cm hng t c&ocirc;ng ngh &quot;<strong>Chia s d liu lp (</strong><strong>Class Data Sharing)</strong>&quot;&nbsp;c thit k cho Java HotSpot VM. N&oacute; nhm mc &iacute;ch cung cp cho ngi d&ugrave;ng kh nng trao i linh hot m&agrave; m&ocirc; h&igrave;nh PHP th&ocirc;ng thng cung cp  tng hiu sut.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Khi khi ng m&aacute;y ch - trc khi bt k m&atilde; ng dng n&agrave;o c chy - ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i c&oacute; th ti mt tp hp c&aacute;c tp PHP nht nh v&agrave;o b nh - v&agrave; l&agrave;m cho ni dung ca ch&uacute;ng &quot;c&oacute; sn vnh vin&quot; cho tt c c&aacute;c y&ecirc;u cu tip theo s c m&aacute;y ch &oacute; phc v.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tt c c&aacute;c h&agrave;m v&agrave; lp c x&aacute;c nh trong c&aacute;c tp n&agrave;y s sn s&agrave;ng c ly ra, ging ht nh c&aacute;c thc th ni b (&nbsp;internal entities) v&iacute; d nh:&nbsp;<code>strlen()</code>&nbsp;hoc&nbsp;<code>Exception</code>.&nbsp;Bng c&aacute;ch n&agrave;y, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i c&oacute; th&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>PRELOAD - ti trc</strong>&nbsp;to&agrave;n b hoc mt phn frameworks v&agrave; thm ch&iacute; to&agrave;n b th vin lp ng dng (application class library).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>N&oacute; cng s cho ph&eacute;p gii thiu c&aacute;c h&agrave;m &quot;t&iacute;ch hp sn&quot; s c vit bng PHP (tng t nh HHVM sytemlib). T&iacute;nh trao i linh hot s bao gm vic kh&ocirc;ng th cp nht c&aacute;c tp n&agrave;y khi m&aacute;y ch &atilde; c khi ng (vic cp nht c&aacute;c tp n&agrave;y tr&ecirc;n h thng tp s kh&ocirc;ng l&agrave;m bt k iu g&igrave;; Khi ng li m&aacute;y ch s c y&ecirc;u cu &aacute;p dng c&aacute;c thay i); Ngo&agrave;i ra, c&aacute;ch tip cn n&agrave;y s&nbsp;<strong>kh&ocirc;ng tng th&iacute;ch vi c&aacute;c m&aacute;y ch lu tr nhiu ng dng hoc nhiu phi&ecirc;n bn ng dng</strong>- v&igrave; s c&oacute;&nbsp;<strong>c&aacute;c lp nht nh c&oacute; c&ugrave;ng t&ecirc;n</strong>&nbsp;- nu c&aacute;c lp &oacute; c ti trc t m&atilde; ca mt ng dng, c&aacute;c ng dng sau &oacute; s c&oacute; kh nng xung t.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>** Chung ngh tng lai s c&oacute; c&aacute;ch gii quyt ng qu&aacute; hoang mang - v&igrave; server ca m&igrave;nh cng ang t nhiu application tr&ecirc;n n&agrave;y (website) **</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>PHP Preload hot ng nh th n&agrave;o</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&Ocirc; k&ecirc;, t&iacute;nh nng preload n&agrave;y s c iu khin bi mt&nbsp;directive c&oacute; t&ecirc;n l&agrave;&nbsp;<strong>opcache.preload</strong>&nbsp; trong file php.ini.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>V&iacute; d di &acirc;y s gii thiu mt helper function v&agrave; s dng n&oacute; &nbsp;<strong>preload</strong>&nbsp;to&agrave;n b Zend framework.</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>&lt;?php\r\nfunction _preload($preload, string $pattern = &quot;/\\.php$/&quot;, array $ignore = []) {\r\n  // nu preload l&agrave; mt mng\r\n  if (is_array($preload)) {\r\n    //  quy  preload tng path\r\n    foreach ($preload as $path) {\r\n      _preload($path, $pattern, $ignore);\r\n    }\r\n  } else if (is_string($preload)) {\r\n    $path = $preload;\r\n    // nu $path kh&ocirc;ng nm trong danh s&aacute;ch t chi th&igrave; preload\r\n    if (!in_array($path, $ignore)) {\r\n      // nu n&oacute; l&agrave; 1 th mc\r\n      if (is_dir($path)) {\r\n        //  quy c ht file .php (ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; $pattern) trong th mc &oacute; v&agrave; preload\r\n        if ($dh = opendir($path)) {\r\n          while (($file = readdir($dh)) !== false) {\r\n            if ($file !== &quot;.&quot; &amp;&amp; $file !== &quot;..&quot;) {\r\n              _preload($path . &quot;/&quot; . $file, $pattern, $ignore);\r\n            }\r\n          }\r\n          closedir($dh);\r\n        }\r\n      // preload file .php\r\n      } else if (is_file($path) &amp;&amp; preg_match($pattern, $path)) {\r\n        if (!opcache_compile_file($path)) {\r\n          trigger_error(&quot;Preloading Failed&quot;, E_USER_ERROR);\r\n        }\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n \r\nset_include_path(get_include_path() . PATH_SEPARATOR . realpath(&quot;/var/www/ZendFramework/library&quot;));\r\n// preload ht code ca Zend framework\r\n_preload([&quot;/var/www/ZendFramework/library&quot;]);</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nh &atilde;  cp  tr&ecirc;n, c&aacute;c tp c ti sn s c lu tr trong b nh opcache m&atilde;i m&atilde;i. Vic sa i c&aacute;c tp ngun tng ng ca ch&uacute;ng s kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; bt k nh hng n&agrave;o m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng cn khi ng li m&aacute;y ch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tt c c&aacute;c h&agrave;m v&agrave; hu ht c&aacute;c lp c nh ngha trong c&aacute;c tp n&agrave;y s c ti vnh vin v&agrave;o c&aacute;c h&agrave;m v&agrave; c&aacute;c lp ca PHP v&agrave; tr n&ecirc;n vnh vin c&oacute; sn trong ng cnh ca bt k y&ecirc;u cu n&agrave;o trong tng lai. (C&oacute; sn ging nh c&aacute;c h&agrave;m core ca PHP)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh ti trc - preload, PHP cng gii quyt c&aacute;c ph thuc lp (class dependencies) v&agrave; c&aacute;c li&ecirc;n kt vi cha m nh c&aacute;c interfaces v&agrave; traits. N&oacute; cng loi b nhng bao gm (include) kh&ocirc;ng cn thit v&agrave; thc hin mt s ti u h&oacute;a kh&aacute;c.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>C&oacute; 2 h&agrave;m cn quan t&acirc;m trong preload &oacute; l&agrave;:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><code>opcache_reset()</code>: h&agrave;m n&agrave;y vn s reset to&agrave;n b opcode cache lu trong opcache, NHNG n&oacute; s kh&ocirc;ng reset c&aacute;c file preload (Nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n l&agrave; reset s dn n crash cho v&agrave;i process kh&aacute;c ang s dng preload)</li>\r\n	<li><code>opcache_get_status()</code>:&nbsp;H&agrave;m n&agrave;y tr v th&ocirc;ng tin trng th&aacute;i v cache&nbsp;instance, th&igrave; b&acirc;y gi n&oacute; s&nbsp;c m rng  cung cp th&ocirc;ng tin v c&aacute;c h&agrave;m, lp v&agrave; tp lnh c preload - (s c bt bi mt index &quot;<em>preload_statistics</em>&quot; n&agrave;o &oacute;)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>S hn ch trong Preloading</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Ch c&aacute;c lp cha c gii quyt (unresolved&nbsp;) m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; cha m, &nbsp;interfaces, traits v&agrave; constant values mi c&oacute; th c ti trc. Nu mt lp kh&ocirc;ng tha m&atilde;n iu kin n&agrave;y, n&oacute; c lu tr trong opcache SHM nh l&agrave; mt phn ca tp lnh PHP tng ng ging nh c&aacute;ch m&agrave; l&uacute;c cha c&oacute; preloading. Ngo&agrave;i ra, ch c&aacute;c thc th cp cao nht kh&ocirc;ng c lng trong cu tr&uacute;c iu khin (v&iacute; d: if() ...) mi c&oacute; th c ti trc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tr&ecirc;n Windows, bn cng kh&ocirc;ng th ti trc c&aacute;c lp c k tha t c&aacute;c lp b&ecirc;n trong.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>C&aacute;c thay i kh&ocirc;ng tng th&iacute;ch ngc (Backward Incompatible)</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Preload</strong>&nbsp;kh&ocirc;ng nh hng n bt k chc nng n&agrave;o tr khi n&oacute; c s dng mt c&aacute;ch r&otilde; r&agrave;ng. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, nu c s dng, n&oacute; c&oacute; th ph&aacute; v mt s h&agrave;nh vi ng dng, bi v&igrave; c&aacute;c lp v&agrave; h&agrave;m c&nbsp;<strong>preload</strong>&nbsp;lu&ocirc;n c&oacute; sn v&agrave; khi c kim tra bng&nbsp;<code>function_exists()</code>&nbsp;hoc&nbsp;<code>class_exists()</code>&nbsp;n&oacute; s lu&ocirc;n tr v&nbsp;<strong>TRUE</strong>, v&agrave; c&oacute; th dn n ngn chn thc thi on code d kin.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nh &atilde;  cp  tr&ecirc;n, vic s dng kh&ocirc;ng &uacute;ng tr&ecirc;n m&aacute;y ch c&oacute; nhiu ng dng cng c&oacute; th dn n li. V&igrave; c&aacute;c ng dng kh&aacute;c nhau (hoc c&aacute;c phi&ecirc;n bn kh&aacute;c nhau ca c&ugrave;ng mt ng dng) c&oacute; th c&oacute; c&ugrave;ng t&ecirc;n class/function trong c&aacute;c file kh&aacute;c nhau, nu mt phi&ecirc;n bn ca lp c preload - n&oacute; s ngn ti bt k phi&ecirc;n bn n&agrave;o kh&aacute;c ca lp &oacute; c nh ngha trong mt file kh&aacute;c.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Phi&ecirc;n bn PHP n&agrave;o s s dng Preload</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>7.4</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>C&oacute; thc s s t tc  b&agrave;n th nh li n?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>S dng preload m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; bt k chnh sa n&agrave;o vi code, khi test&nbsp;ZF1_HelloWorld s t 3620 request tr&ecirc;n 1 gi&acirc;y so vi 2650 khi cha c&oacute; preload.&nbsp;(3620 req/sec vs 2650 req/sec) Nh vy hiu sut &atilde; gia tng khong 30%</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tng t vi ZF2Test thu c (1300 req/sec vs 670 req/sec)&nbsp;&rArr; c&ocirc;ng lc tng 50%</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, tc  thc t s ph thuc v&agrave;o t l gia chi ph&iacute; khi ng ca code v&agrave; thi gian chy ca code, v&agrave; c&oacute; th s thp hn (<strong>tc l&agrave; s hn con s 30 50% kia nh&eacute;</strong>). iu n&agrave;y c&oacute; th s mang li nhng li &iacute;ch &aacute;ng ch&uacute; &yacute; nht vi c&aacute;c y&ecirc;u cu vi thi gian rt ngn, chng hn nh c&aacute;c microservices (Lumen, ...).</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Nhng vn  c x&eacute;t ti trong tng lai</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Vic np trc c&oacute; th c s dng nh HHVM&nbsp;systemlib  nh ngha c&aacute;c h&agrave;m / lp &quot;chun&quot; trong PHP</li>\r\n	<li>C&oacute; th bi&ecirc;n dch trc preload script v&agrave; s dng biu mu nh ph&acirc;n (perfect nh l&agrave; .so hoc .dll lu&ocirc;n )  tng tc m&aacute;y ch khi ng.</li>\r\n	<li>C&ugrave;ng vi ext/FFI (phn m rng nguy him), ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i ch c&oacute; th cho ph&eacute;p chc nng FFI trong c&aacute;c tp PHP c preload, nhng kh&ocirc;ng cho ph&eacute;p trong c&aacute;c tp th&ocirc;ng thng</li>\r\n	<li>C&oacute; th thc hin ti u h&oacute;a t&iacute;ch cc hn v&agrave; to m&atilde; JIT tt hn cho c&aacute;c h&agrave;m v&agrave; lp c ti sn (tng t nh HHVM Repo Authoritative mode trong HHVM)</li>\r\n	<li>N&oacute; s l&agrave; tuyt vi (hn l&agrave; tuyt vi ri ahihi ),  m rng mt s loi c ch trin khai, cp nht c&aacute;c g&oacute;i c preload m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng cn khi ng li m&aacute;y ch.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Kt qu ca  xut Preload</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>48/48 phiu bu t&aacute;n th&agrave;nh  xut n&agrave;y n&oacute;i l&ecirc;n tt c, PHP linh hot, mnh m v&agrave; gi &acirc;y n&oacute; c gia tng th&ecirc;m mt phn c&ocirc;ng lc na &oacute; l&agrave;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>SPEEDDDDDDDDD&nbsp;</strong></p>', 'PHP 7.4: Preload - Tc  bn th cho PHP - Ho Minh Blog', 'PHP 7.4: Preload - Tc  bn th cho PHP - Ho Minh Blog', 'PHP 7.4: Preload - Tc  bn th cho PHP - Ho Minh Blog', '/photos/1/php-7-4-preload-toc-do-ban-tho-cho-php-medium.jpg', 1, 2, 1, '2018-11-15 19:42:56', '2018-11-15 19:42:56'),
(11, 'Lch s Laravel', 'lich-su-laravel', 3, 1, 'Laravel l mt PHP web framework min ph, m ngun m, c to ra bi Taylor Otwell v d nh pht trin cc ng dng web theo m hnh kin trc modelviewcontroller (MVC) v da trn Symfony.', '<p><strong>Laravel</strong>&nbsp;l&agrave; mt&nbsp;<strong>PHP web framework</strong>&nbsp;min ph&iacute;, m&atilde; ngun m, c to ra bi Taylor Otwell v&agrave; d nh ph&aacute;t trin c&aacute;c ng dng web theo m&ocirc; h&igrave;nh kin tr&uacute;c model&ndash;view&ndash;controller (MVC) v&agrave; da tr&ecirc;n Symfony.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Th&ocirc;ng tin c bn</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Developer(s):&nbsp;<a href=\"https://twitter.com/taylorotwell\" target=\"_blank\">Taylor Otwell</a></li>\r\n	<li>Ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh ln u: June 2011; 7 years ago[1]</li>\r\n	<li>Phi&ecirc;n bn n nh: 5.7.2 September 6, 2018</li>\r\n	<li>Repository:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/laravel/framework\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/laravel/framework</a></li>\r\n	<li>Vit bi: PHP 7</li>\r\n	<li>Loi: Web framework</li>\r\n	<li>License: MIT License</li>\r\n	<li>Website:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/laravel.com\" target=\"_blank\">laravel.com</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Lch s Laravel</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Taylor Otwell &atilde; to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/go/5bgvy7\"><strong>Laravel</strong></a>&nbsp;nh mt n lc  cung cp mt gii ph&aacute;p thay th n&acirc;ng cao hn cho CodeIgniter framework,&nbsp;v&igrave; n&oacute; kh&ocirc;ng cung cp mt s t&iacute;nh nng nht nh nh l&agrave; h tr t&iacute;ch hp x&aacute;c thc (authentication) v&agrave; y quyn (authorization) ngi d&ugrave;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Bn ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh beta u ti&ecirc;n ca Laravel</strong>&nbsp;c ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh v&agrave;o&nbsp;<strong>ng&agrave;y 9 th&aacute;ng 6 nm 2011</strong>, tip theo l&agrave; bn ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh&nbsp;<strong>Laravel 1</strong>&nbsp;sau &oacute; trong c&ugrave;ng mt th&aacute;ng. Laravel 1 bao gm h tr t&iacute;ch hp cho x&aacute;c thc, bn a h&oacute;a (localisation), models, views, sessions, nh tuyn (routing) v&agrave; c&aacute;c c ch kh&aacute;c, nhng thiu h tr cho c&aacute;c b iu khin (controller) ngn cn n&oacute; tr th&agrave;nh mt MVC framework thc s.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Laravel 2</strong>&nbsp;c ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh v&agrave;o&nbsp;<strong>th&aacute;ng 9 nm 2011</strong>&nbsp;(3 th&aacute;ng sau&nbsp;), mang li nhiu ci tin kh&aacute;c nhau t t&aacute;c gi v&agrave; cng ng. C&aacute;c t&iacute;nh nng ch&iacute;nh mi bao gm s h tr cho c&aacute;c b iu khin (controller), n&oacute; &atilde; l&agrave;m cho Laravel 2 tr th&agrave;nh mt framework tu&acirc;n th y  MVC, h tr sn cho nguy&ecirc;n l&yacute; iu khin (IoC) v&agrave; mt h thng templating gi l&agrave; Blade. Nhc im, h tr cho c&aacute;c g&oacute;i ca b&ecirc;n th ba (third-party packages) &atilde; c g b trong Laravel 2.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Laravel 3</strong>&nbsp;c ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh v&agrave;o&nbsp;<strong>th&aacute;ng 2 nm 2012</strong>&nbsp;vi mt lot c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh nng mi bao gm giao din d&ograve;ng lnh -&nbsp;command-line interface (CLI) c&oacute; t&ecirc;n&nbsp;<strong>Artisan</strong>, h tr sn cho nhiu h thng qun l&yacute; c s d liu, database migrations, h tr x l&yacute; events v&agrave; h thng &oacute;ng g&oacute;i c gi l&agrave; Bundles. K t bc nhy vt  phi&ecirc;n bn n&agrave;y, ta chng kin s gia tng ngi d&ugrave;ng (developer) v&agrave; mc  ph bin ca Laravel tng ch&oacute;ng mt.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Laravel 4</strong>, c t t&ecirc;n l&agrave;&nbsp;<strong>Illuminate</strong>&nbsp;, c ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh v&agrave;o&nbsp;<strong>th&aacute;ng 5 nm 2013</strong>. N&oacute; c vit th&agrave;nh mt khung ho&agrave;n chnh ca&nbsp;<strong>Laravel framework</strong>, di chuyn b cc ca n&oacute; th&agrave;nh mt tp c&aacute;c g&oacute;i ri&ecirc;ng bit c ph&acirc;n phi th&ocirc;ng qua&nbsp;<a href=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/go/Tl5p32\"><strong>Composer</strong></a>, phc v nh mt tr&igrave;nh qun l&yacute; g&oacute;i ng dng. C&aacute;ch b tr&iacute; nh vy &atilde; ci thin kh nng m rng ca Laravel 4. C&aacute;c t&iacute;nh nng mi kh&aacute;c trong bn ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh Laravel 4 bao gm database seeding, h tr h&agrave;ng i (queue) tin nhn, h tr cho vic gi c&aacute;c loi email kh&aacute;c nhau v&agrave; h tr x&oacute;a c&aacute;c bn ghi c s d liu dng SoftDelete (kh&ocirc;ng x&oacute;a hn khi database).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Laravel 5</strong>&nbsp;c ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh v&agrave;o&nbsp;<strong>th&aacute;ng 2 nm 2015</strong>&nbsp;l&agrave; kt qu ca nhng thay i ni b &atilde; kt th&uacute;c trong vic thay i bn ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh Laravel 4.3 trong tng lai. C&aacute;c t&iacute;nh nng mi trong bn ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh Laravel 5 bao gm h tr lp k hoch (scheduling) c&aacute;c t&aacute;c v c thc hin nh k th&ocirc;ng qua g&oacute;i c&oacute; t&ecirc;n&nbsp;<strong>Scheduler</strong>, mt lp tru tng (abstraction layer) c&oacute; t&ecirc;n&nbsp;<strong>Flysystem</strong>&nbsp;cho ph&eacute;p lu tr t xa c&aacute;ch d&ugrave;ng tng t nh tr&ecirc;n local, ci thin vic x l&yacute; t&agrave;i sn g&oacute;i th&ocirc;ng qua&nbsp;<strong>Elixir</strong>&nbsp;(gi i t&ecirc;n th&agrave;nh&nbsp;<a href=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/go/32dmZZ\"><strong>Laravel Mix</strong></a>), h tr x&aacute;c thc b&ecirc;n th 3 n gin th&ocirc;ng qua g&oacute;i Socialite (xem th&ecirc;m&nbsp;<a href=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/go/sDukJw\"><strong>Laravel ng nhp th&ocirc;ng qua c&aacute;c mng x&atilde; hi Facebook, Google, Twitter, Github</strong></a>). Laravel 5 cng gii thiu cu tr&uacute;c c&acirc;y th mc mi (<strong><a href=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/go/vqWlO1\">T&igrave;m hiu cu tr&uacute;c th mc ca Laravel</a></strong>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/go/0Vs4sU\"><strong>Laravel 5.7 Thay i cu tr&uacute;c th mc Resources</strong></a>) cho c&aacute;c ng dng &atilde; ph&aacute;t trin.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>V&agrave;o th&aacute;ng 3 nm 2015, mt kho s&aacute;t SitePoint &atilde; lit k&ecirc; Laravel l&agrave; PHP framework ph bin nht.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Laravel 5.1</strong>, ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh v&agrave;o th&aacute;ng 6 nm 2015, l&agrave; bn ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh u ti&ecirc;n ca Laravel  nhn h tr d&agrave;i hn (LTS), vi c&aacute;c bn sa li c&oacute; sn trong hai nm v&agrave; c&aacute;c bn v&aacute; bo mt trong ba nm. Bn ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh LTS ca Laravel c l&ecirc;n k hoch ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh hai nm mt ln.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Laravel 5.3</strong>, c ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh v&agrave;o ng&agrave;y 23 th&aacute;ng 8 nm 2016. C&aacute;c t&iacute;nh nng mi trong 5.3 tp trung v&agrave;o vic ci thin tc  ph&aacute;t trin bng c&aacute;ch b sung th&ecirc;m c&aacute;c ci tin cho c&aacute;c t&aacute;c v ph bin.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Laravel 5.4</strong>&nbsp;Phi&ecirc;n bn n&agrave;y c&oacute; nhiu t&iacute;nh nng mi, nh Laravel Dusk, Laravel Mix, Blade Components v&agrave; Slots, Markdown Emails, Automatic Facades, Route Improvements, Higher Order Messaging cho Collections, v&agrave; nhiu th kh&aacute;c.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Laravel 5.5</strong>, ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh v&agrave;o ng&agrave;y 30 th&aacute;ng 8 nm 2017 l&agrave; phi&ecirc;n bn LTS th 2 (<a href=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/go/laKO2w\"><strong>Laravel 5.5 s l&agrave; phi&ecirc;n bn LTS Release tip theo</strong></a>).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Laravel 5.6</strong>, ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh v&agrave;o ng&agrave;y 7 th&aacute;ng 2 nm 2018.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Laravel 5.7</strong>, ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh v&agrave;o ng&agrave;y 4 th&aacute;ng 9 nm 2018 vi nhng cp nht.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/go/E5f6Il\"><strong>Laravel 5.7 Ci thin th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o li</strong></a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/go/CKLudK\"><strong>Laravel 5.7 Callable Action URLs</strong></a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/go/TgeidG\"><strong>Laravel 5.7 Email Verification</strong></a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/go/YVH7Mz\"><strong>Laravel 5.7: B sung phng thc mi cho t&ugrave;y chnh ph&acirc;n trang</strong></a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/go/0Vs4sU\"><strong>Laravel 5.7 Thay i cu tr&uacute;c th mc Resources</strong></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Laravel release history</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Tng kt li bng c&aacute;i bng n&agrave;y nh&eacute;</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>Version</th>\r\n			<th>Release date</th>\r\n			<th>PHP version</th>\r\n			<th>Notes</th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>1.0</th>\r\n			<td>June 2011</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>NA</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>2.0</th>\r\n			<td>September 2011</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>NA</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>3.0</th>\r\n			<td>February 22, 2012</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>NA</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>3.1</th>\r\n			<td>March 27, 2012</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>NA</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>3.2</th>\r\n			<td>May 22, 2012</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>NA</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>4.0</th>\r\n			<td>May 28, 2013</td>\r\n			<td>&ge; 5.3.0</td>\r\n			<td>NA</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>4.1</th>\r\n			<td>December 12, 2013</td>\r\n			<td>&ge; 5.3.0</td>\r\n			<td>NA</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>4.2</th>\r\n			<td>June 1, 2014</td>\r\n			<td>&ge; 5.4.0</td>\r\n			<td>NA</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>5.0</th>\r\n			<td>February 4, 2015</td>\r\n			<td>&ge; 5.4.0</td>\r\n			<td>NA</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>5.1 LTS</th>\r\n			<td>June 9, 2015</td>\r\n			<td>&ge; 5.5.9</td>\r\n			<td>NA</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>5.2</th>\r\n			<td>December 21, 2015</td>\r\n			<td>&ge; 5.5.9</td>\r\n			<td>NA</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>5.3</th>\r\n			<td>August 23, 2016</td>\r\n			<td>&ge; 5.6.4</td>\r\n			<td>NA</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>5.4</th>\r\n			<td>January 24, 2017</td>\r\n			<td>&ge; 5.6.4</td>\r\n			<td>NA</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>5.5 LTS</th>\r\n			<td>August 30, 2017</td>\r\n			<td>&ge; 7.0.0</td>\r\n			<td>NA</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>5.6</th>\r\n			<td>February 7, 2018</td>\r\n			<td>&ge; 7.1.3</td>\r\n			<td>NA</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>5.7</th>\r\n			<td>September 4, 2018</td>\r\n			<td>&ge; 7.1.3</td>\r\n			<td>NA</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Lch s Laravel - Ho Minh Blog', 'Lch s Laravel - Ho Minh Blog', 'Lch s Laravel - Ho Minh Blog', '/photos/1/lich-su-laravel-medium.jpg', 1, 0, 1, '2018-11-16 19:56:33', '2018-11-16 19:56:33'),
(12, '[Laravel Sitemap] To sitemap - s  web cho website laravel', '[laravel-sitemap]-tao-sitemap---so-do-web-cho-website-laravel', 3, 1, 'Sitemap hay cn gi l s  trang web theo ng nh tn gi sitemap ging nh l mt bn  thu nh tp hp cc ng dn URL ca mt trang web, h tr iu hng hnh vi ca ngi dng trn website ng thi cn gip cho con Bot ca Google d thu thp d liu v nh ch mc website ca bn.', '<h2>1. Sitemap l&agrave; g&igrave;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Sitemap hay c&ograve;n gi l&agrave; s  trang web theo &uacute;ng nh t&ecirc;n gi sitemap ging nh l&agrave; mt bn  thu nh tp hp c&aacute;c ng dn URL ca mt trang web, h tr iu hng h&agrave;nh vi ca ngi d&ugrave;ng tr&ecirc;n website ng thi c&ograve;n gi&uacute;p cho con&nbsp;<code>Bot ca Google</code>&nbsp;d thu thp d liu v&agrave; &aacute;nh ch mc website ca bn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/photos/1/sitemap1.png\" style=\"height:529px; width:918px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>u bn ang l&agrave;m&nbsp;<strong>SEO</strong>&nbsp;hay ang t&igrave;m hiu v&nbsp;<strong>SEO</strong>&nbsp;th&igrave;&nbsp;<strong>Sitemap</strong>&nbsp;l&agrave; mt yu t kh&ocirc;ng th b qua cho bt k 1 website n&agrave;o. Trc khi i v&agrave;o to sitemap bn phi hiu r&otilde; c bn cht c im ca n&oacute; l&agrave; g&igrave;, li &iacute;ch m&agrave; n&oacute; mang li i vi qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh SEO nh th n&agrave;o?</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>2. T&aacute;c dng ca sitemap i vi SEO</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>To sitemap l&agrave; vic quan trng i vi bt k 1 website n&agrave;o, tuy n&oacute; kh&ocirc;ng nh hng trc tip n th hng ca website nhng n&oacute; s gi&uacute;p iu hng h&agrave;nh vi ngi d&ugrave;ng mt c&aacute;ch tt nht, th&acirc;n thin vi c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng c t&igrave;m kim:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/photos/1/sitemap2.jpg\" style=\"height:325px; width:459px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sitemap gi&uacute;p khai b&aacute;o cho c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng c t&igrave;m kim (Google, Yahoo, Bing, Coccoc, v..v) bit c&nbsp;<strong>s  c&aacute;c li&ecirc;n kt trong website</strong>&nbsp;gi&uacute;p cho vic&nbsp;<strong>lp ch mc</strong>&nbsp;din ra mt c&aacute;ch d d&agrave;ng v&agrave; ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Ci thin tc  index cho website</strong>: Vic to 1 sitemap s gi&uacute;p bn gia tng tc  index mt c&aacute;ch nhanh ch&oacute;ng c&aacute;c trang tr&ecirc;n site</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Ph&aacute;t hin c c&aacute;c li li&ecirc;n kt (404, 500 ...)</strong>:&nbsp;<strong>Google bot</strong>&nbsp;gp phi li kh&ocirc;ng thu thp th&ocirc;ng tin cng l&agrave; chuyn kh&ocirc;ng th tr&aacute;nh khi. Khi to sitemap bn s kim so&aacute;t c&aacute;c li&ecirc;n kt li mt c&aacute;ch d d&agrave;ng hn</li>\r\n	<li>C&aacute;c nh&agrave; qun tr website c&oacute; th qun l&yacute; h thng ca m&igrave;nh mt c&aacute;ch tng quan ph&acirc;n cp ni dung tr&ecirc;n trang mt c&aacute;ch ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Site map c&oacute; 2 loi, loi th nht l&agrave; xml, loi th 2 l&agrave; html. Trong b&agrave;i n&agrave;y t&ocirc;i s gii thiu cho bn c&aacute;ch to file sitemap bng xml:</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>&lt;url&gt;\r\n    &lt;loc&gt;\r\n        https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/tao-sitemap-so-do-web-cho-website-laravel\r\n    &lt;/loc&gt;\r\n    &lt;priority&gt;1&lt;/priority&gt;\r\n    &lt;lastmod&gt;2018-06-14T08:57:48+07:00&lt;/lastmod&gt;\r\n    &lt;changefreq&gt;daily&lt;/changefreq&gt;\r\n&lt;/url&gt;\r\n&lt;url&gt;\r\n    &lt;loc&gt;\r\n        https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/laravel-nginx-loai-bo-index-php-tren-url-toi-uu-seo\r\n    &lt;/loc&gt;\r\n    &lt;priority&gt;1&lt;/priority&gt;\r\n    &lt;lastmod&gt;2018-06-08T21:16:46+07:00&lt;/lastmod&gt;\r\n    &lt;changefreq&gt;daily&lt;/changefreq&gt;\r\n&lt;/url&gt;</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<h2>3. To sitemap file bng code laravel</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Thc ra to sitemap file c&oacute; nhiu website tr&ecirc;n mng h tr bn l&agrave;m vic n&agrave;y, nhng im bt li ca n&oacute; l&agrave; n&oacute; gii hn  ln website ca bn (tc l&agrave; ch c ti a bao nhi&ecirc;u link tr&ecirc;n b&agrave;i vit), hay l&agrave; mi khi website ca bn c&oacute; b&agrave;i mi n&oacute; s kh&ocirc;ng t ng cp nhp v&agrave;o sitemap, s rt bt tin khi ln n&agrave;o cng s phi l&ecirc;n website &oacute; ri to sitemap xong download v ri li upload l&ecirc;n host ca m&igrave;nh &uacute;ng kh&ocirc;ng n&agrave;o.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mt sitemap t ng bng code vi bt k ng link n&agrave;o bn mun, v&agrave; bn c&oacute; th t lch cho n&oacute; chy hng ng&agrave;y ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n t ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong b&agrave;i n&agrave;y t&ocirc;i s d&ugrave;ng&nbsp;<strong>th vin laravel-sitemap</strong>&nbsp;ca t&aacute;c gi RoumenDamianoff c&aacute;c bn c&oacute; th tham kho ti y&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/RoumenDamianoff/laravel-sitemap\">https://github.com/RoumenDamianoff/laravel-sitemap</a>&nbsp;.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>A. C&agrave;i t th vin</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Lu &yacute;:&nbsp;Laravel 5.5 tr l&ecirc;n kh&ocirc;ng phi l&agrave;m bc 2 v&agrave; 3</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Bn m terminal l&ecirc;n chy lnh sau:&nbsp;<code>composer require roumen/sitemap</code>&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Add v&agrave;o service Provider d&ograve;ng sau:&nbsp;<code>Roumen\\Sitemap\\SitemapServiceProvider::class,</code></li>\r\n	<li>Chy lnh&nbsp;<code>php artisan vendor:publish --provider=&quot;Roumen\\Sitemap\\SitemapServiceProvider&quot;</code>&nbsp; pubic nhng file config.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Nh vy ch&uacute;ng ra &atilde; c&agrave;i t xong th vin, tip theo ch&uacute;ng ta s to sitemap cho website. C&oacute; 2 c&aacute;ch  to ra laravel sitemap ca bn t&ugrave;y v&agrave;o  ln ca website v&agrave; iu kin bn c&oacute; s hu VPS ri&ecirc;ng hay kh&ocirc;ng?</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>B1. To Laravel sitemap bng c&aacute;ch xut ra file xml</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>IU KIN: S HU VPS HOC HOSTING C&Oacute; TH CHY C CRONJOB  CHY T NG HOC CHY TH C&Ocirc;NG DI LOCAL RI UPLOAD FILE XML L&Ecirc;N HOSTING</p>\r\n\r\n<p>u ti&ecirc;n bn chy lnh sau trong terminal:&nbsp;<code>php artisan make:command CreateSiteMap --command=sitemap:create</code>&nbsp;lnh n&agrave;y s to ra 1 file l&agrave;&nbsp;<code>CreateSiteMap.php</code>&nbsp;trong th mc&nbsp;<code>app/console/commands</code>&nbsp;c&oacute; ni dung nh sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>&lt;?php\r\n\r\nnamespace App\\Console\\Commands;\r\n\r\nuse Illuminate\\Console\\Command;\r\n\r\nclass CreateSiteMap extends Command\r\n{\r\n    /**\r\n     * The name and signature of the console command.\r\n     *\r\n     * @var string\r\n     */\r\n    protected $signature = &#39;sitemap:create&#39;;\r\n\r\n    /**\r\n     * The console command description.\r\n     *\r\n     * @var string\r\n     */\r\n    protected $description = &#39;Command description&#39;;\r\n\r\n    /**\r\n     * Create a new command instance.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return void\r\n     */\r\n    public function __construct()\r\n    {\r\n        parent::__construct();\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    /**\r\n     * Execute the console command.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return mixed\r\n     */\r\n    public function handle()\r\n    {\r\n        //\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>H&agrave;m handle s c vit li th sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>public function handle()\r\n{\r\n    $sitemap = \\App::make(&#39;sitemap&#39;);\r\n    // add home pages mc nh\r\n    $sitemap-&gt;add(\\URL::to(&#39;/&#39;), \\Carbon::now(), 1, &#39;daily&#39;);\r\n\r\n    // add b&agrave;i vit\r\n    $posts = \\DB::table(&#39;blog_posts&#39;)-&gt;orderBy(&#39;created_at&#39;, &#39;desc&#39;)-&gt;get();\r\n    foreach ($posts as $post) {\r\n        //$sitemap-&gt;add(url, thi gian,  u ti&ecirc;n, thi gian quay li)\r\n        $sitemap-&gt;add(route(&#39;post.show&#39;, $post-&gt;slug), $post-&gt;updated_at, 1, &#39;daily&#39;);\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    // lu file v&agrave; ph&acirc;n quyn\r\n    $sitemap-&gt;store(&#39;xml&#39;, &#39;sitemap&#39;);\r\n    if (\\File::exists(public_path(&#39;sitemap.xml&#39;))) {\r\n        chmod(public_path(&#39;sitemap.xml&#39;), 0777);\r\n    }\r\n}</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong th mc ca project ca bn chy lnh sau:&nbsp;<code>php artisan sitemap:create</code>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>G&otilde; tr&ecirc;n tr&igrave;nh duyt&nbsp;<code>yourdomain.com/sitemap.xml</code>&nbsp;nu thy xut hin th n&agrave;y tc l&agrave; bn &atilde; th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/photos/1/sitemap3.png\" style=\"height:770px; width:825px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nh vy l&agrave; xong c&aacute;ch to sitemap bng code hon to&agrave;n t ng, b&acirc;y gi bn c&oacute; th config cronjob tr&ecirc;n server ca bn  n&oacute; chy hng ng&agrave;y hoc hng tun nu bn mun.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Config&nbsp;cronjob chy t ng tr&ecirc;n server</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>bt editor cronjob tr&ecirc;n vps:&nbsp;<code>EDITOR=nano crontab -e</code></li>\r\n	<li>add cronjob (thay ng dn n file artisan nha):&nbsp;<code>* * * * * php /home/chungnguyen.xyz/public_html/artisan schedule:run &gt;&gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1</code></li>\r\n	<li>Trong file:&nbsp;<code>\\app\\Console\\Kernel.php</code>&nbsp;function&nbsp;<code>schedule()</code>&nbsp;th&ecirc;m lch chy command</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<pre>\r\n<code>&lt;?php\r\n\r\nnamespace App\\Console;\r\n\r\nuse Illuminate\\Console\\Scheduling\\Schedule;\r\nuse Illuminate\\Foundation\\Console\\Kernel as ConsoleKernel;\r\n\r\nclass Kernel extends ConsoleKernel\r\n{\r\n    /**\r\n     * The Artisan commands provided by your application.\r\n     *\r\n     * @var array\r\n     */\r\n    protected $commands = [\r\n        Commands\\CreateSiteMap::class,\r\n        //\r\n    ];\r\n\r\n    /**\r\n     * Define the application&#39;s command schedule.\r\n     *\r\n     * @param  \\Illuminate\\Console\\Scheduling\\Schedule  $schedule\r\n     * @return void\r\n     */\r\n    protected function schedule(Schedule $schedule)\r\n    {\r\n        $schedule-&gt;command(&#39;sitemap:create&#39;)-&gt;dailyAt(&#39;1:00&#39;);\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    /**\r\n     * Register the commands for the application.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return void\r\n     */\r\n    protected function commands()\r\n    {\r\n        $this-&gt;load(__DIR__.&#39;/Commands&#39;);\r\n\r\n        require base_path(&#39;routes/console.php&#39;);\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n	<p>Copy</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Sitemap s c to t ng mi ng&agrave;y v&agrave;o l&uacute;c 1h s&aacute;ng, bn ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n c&oacute; th t&ugrave;y &yacute; chnh dailyAt th&agrave;nh thi gian bn mong mun, nu vy&nbsp;<a href=\"https://laravel.com/docs/master/scheduling#schedule-frequency-options\" target=\"_blank\">xem th&ecirc;m t&agrave;i liu  &acirc;y</a>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h3>B2. To Laravel sitemap trc tip tr&ecirc;n url</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong&nbsp;<code>...\\routes\\web.php</code>&nbsp;th&ecirc;m&nbsp;Route::get(&#39;sitemap&#39;, &#39;HomeController@sitemap&#39;);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong&nbsp;<code>...\\app\\Http\\Controllers\\HomeController.php</code>&nbsp;function&nbsp;<code>sitemap()</code></p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>public function sitemap()\r\n{\r\n    $sitemap = app()-&gt;make(&#39;sitemap&#39;);\r\n\r\n    // Cache kt qu 60 ph&uacute;t\r\n    $sitemap-&gt;setCache(&#39;chungnguyenblog.sitemap.index&#39;, 60);\r\n    if (!$sitemap-&gt;isCached()) {\r\n        $sitemap-&gt;add(url(&#39;/&#39;), \\Carbon::now(), 1, &#39;daily&#39;);\r\n        // add b&agrave;i vit\r\n        $posts = \\DB::table(&#39;blog_posts&#39;)-&gt;orderBy(&#39;created_at&#39;, &#39;desc&#39;)-&gt;get();\r\n        foreach ($posts as $post) {\r\n            //$sitemap-&gt;add(url, thi gian,  u ti&ecirc;n, thi gian quay li)\r\n            $sitemap-&gt;add(route(&#39;post.show&#39;, $post-&gt;slug), $post-&gt;updated_at, 1, &#39;daily&#39;);\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    // show your sitemap (options: &#39;xml&#39; (default), &#39;html&#39;, &#39;txt&#39;, &#39;ror-rss&#39;, &#39;ror-rdf&#39;)\r\n    return $sitemap-&gt;render(&#39;xml&#39;);\r\n}</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>G&otilde; tr&ecirc;n tr&igrave;nh duyt&nbsp;<code>yourdomain.com/sitemap</code>&nbsp;nu thy xut hin th n&agrave;y tc l&agrave; bn &atilde; th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng!</p>', 'PHP: khc nhau trong kt hp mng bng array merge v + - Ho Minh Blog[Laravel Sitemap] To sitemap - s  web cho website laravel', 'PHP: khc nhau trong kt hp mng bng array merge v + - Ho Minh Blog[Laravel Sitemap] To sitemap - s  web cho website laravel', 'PHP: khc nhau trong kt hp mng bng array merge v + - Ho Minh Blog[Laravel Sitemap] To sitemap - s  web cho website laravel', '/photos/1/laravel-sitemap-medium.jpg', 1, 3, 1, '2018-11-18 19:31:05', '2018-11-18 19:31:05'),
(13, 'Composer, cng c tuyt vi dnh cho PHP', 'composer,-cong-cu-tuyet-voi-danh-cho-php', 6, 1, 'Trc khi Composer ra i, chng ta thng kh chu vi hng t cc th vin ca bn th ba cn phi qun', '<p>Composer, c&ocirc;ng c tuyt vi d&agrave;nh cho PHPComposer, c&ocirc;ng c tuyt vi d&agrave;nh cho PHPComposer, c&ocirc;ng c tuyt vi d&agrave;nh cho PHPComposer, c&ocirc;ng c tuyt vi d&agrave;nh cho PHP</p>', 'Composer,cng c tuyt vi dnh cho PHP - Ho Minh Blog', 'Composer,cng c tuyt vi dnh cho PHP - Ho Minh Blog', 'Composer,cng c tuyt vi dnh cho PHP - Ho Minh Blog', '/photos/1/composer-php-medium.jpg', 1, 2, 1, '2018-11-21 20:43:19', '2018-11-21 20:43:19');
