(14, '8 JS frameworks nh xinh cho bn i gi', '8-js-frameworks-nho-xinh-cho-ban-doi-gio', 9, 1, 'Pha sau showbiz ho nhong, hn lon v y th phi, vn c nhng em gi qu nh nhn hin lnh d thng, t i hi ang ch bn...', '<p>V&agrave;o nhng nm 2000, c&aacute;c th vin jQuery, Mootools, Dojo... &atilde; tng l&agrave; cu tinh ca developer, gi&uacute;p h cm c vi kh nng tng th&iacute;ch trong mt k nguy&ecirc;n cha c&oacute; web standard. im nhn ca ca nhng c&ocirc;ng c n&agrave;y l&agrave; DOM Manipulation, Event Listener, Features Detection v&agrave; AJAX. Ch&uacute;ng to ra 1 lp abstraction lp y s ngn c&aacute;ch gia c&aacute;c tr&igrave;nh duyt.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nm 2010 l&agrave; mt nm c&aacute;ch mng, &aacute;nh du bc ngot ln trong th gii front-end: s ra i ca h&agrave;ng lot framework th h mi, trong &oacute; c&oacute; phi k n b t&nbsp;<a href=\"http://backbonejs.org/\">BackboneJS</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://angularjs.org/\">AngularJS</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://knockoutjs.com/\">Knockout</a>&nbsp;v&agrave;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://sproutcore.com/\">SproutCore</a>. T&iacute;nh t ph&aacute; ca ch&uacute;ng nm  nhng kh&aacute;i nim mi m: Data Binding, Templating... c bit l&agrave; c&aacute;c bin th ca kin tr&uacute;c MV-W(hatever) ly cm hng t m&ocirc; h&igrave;nh MVC ph&iacute;a server. Vi Templating v&agrave; two-ways Data Binding, ngi ta ri khi DOM v&agrave; c&aacute;c tr&igrave;nh x l&yacute; s kin  hng v&agrave;o d&ograve;ng chy ca d liu. S bin i ca d liu trong Model s t ng phn chiu ra ngo&agrave;i View.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>T na cui 2015 tr i, th gii tin v&agrave;o thi k ca Web Component, Shadow DOM, virtual/incremental DOM, Progressive Web Apps... &aacute;nh du bi s xut hin ca&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/Polymer/polymer\">Polymer</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/react\">React</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/cyclejs/cyclejs\">Circle.js</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/vuejs/vue\">Vue</a>... AngularJS cng nhanh ch&oacute;ng cho ra mt&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular\">Angular</a>&nbsp;phi&ecirc;n bn mi, trong khi Rob Eisenberg v&agrave; mt v&agrave;i th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n ri nh&oacute;m  ph&aacute;t trin&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/aurelia/framework\">Aurelia</a>&nbsp;theo trit l&yacute; ri&ecirc;ng ca h.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Giai on n&agrave;y cng bt u tr&agrave;o lu Functional v&agrave; Reactive Programming. Nhng ngi ph&aacute;t trin bt u lu &yacute; n t&iacute;nh c&aacute;ch Functional v&agrave; Reactive ca chng tr&igrave;nh. Do &oacute; &atilde; sinh ra nhiu th vin h tr:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/ReactiveX/rxjs\">rxjs</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/ramda/ramda\">Ramda</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/baconjs/bacon.js\">Bacon.js</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/cujojs/most\">Most.js</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/origamitower/folktale\">Folktale</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/sanctuary-js/sanctuary\">Sanctuary</a>... Tuy nhi&ecirc;n phn &ocirc;ng vn trung th&agrave;nh vi&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/jashkenas/underscore\">Underscore.js</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/lodash/lodash\">Lodash</a>... c&oacute; t c&aacute;ch mng 2010.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>C&aacute;c k thut Data Binding v&agrave; Templating vn c &aacute;p dng nhng gia tng x l&yacute; logic v&agrave; real DOM thng c&oacute; th&ecirc;m 1 tng virtual DOM na tn ti. T &oacute; ny sinh c&aacute;c gii ph&aacute;p HyperScript v&agrave; JSX  vit template.  phng din kh&aacute;c, s ph&acirc;n t&aacute;ch Model - View kh&ocirc;ng cn c nhn mnh. Di quan im v Web Component, iu n&agrave;y din ra t nhi&ecirc;n. Mi th u l&agrave; component, mi component c&oacute; phn hin th ra ngo&agrave;i v&agrave; phn logic x l&yacute; b&ecirc;n trong, c&ograve;n data c cha trong c&aacute;c store, c&oacute; th d d&agrave;ng np v&agrave;o component.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hin nay, biu  trending vn ang ng h React v&agrave; Vue, ri Angular, Ember... Nhu cu tuyn dng ch yu xoay quanh 3 c&aacute;i t&ecirc;n n&agrave;y. Trong khi Angular ang dn b tht sng d&ugrave; vn kh&ocirc;ng ngng vt v&atilde; t l&agrave;m mi. React, Vue li rt c y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch nh th mnh vt tri v performance v&agrave; t&iacute;nh linh hot trong kin tr&uacute;c. C 2 ch tp trung v&agrave;o x l&yacute; phn View, d&ugrave;ng virtual DOM v&agrave; template syntax ri&ecirc;ng  render v&agrave; update giao din ngi d&ugrave;ng cui. Do &oacute; ch&uacute;ng c gi l&agrave; UI framework. Tng data s do mt b x l&yacute; kh&aacute;c (vuex, redux...) qu&aacute;n xuyn, t&ugrave;y theo s th&iacute;ch ca developer trong vic x&acirc;y dng v&agrave; thit k chng tr&igrave;nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>JS frameworks hin nay c&ograve;n 1 im chung ni bt na l&agrave; ch&uacute;ng lu&ocirc;n c&oacute; h sinh th&aacute;i ri&ecirc;ng. i k&egrave;m vi core framework l&agrave; nhng cli tool, dev tool, test tool, deploy tool, starter kit v&agrave; nhiu  ngh lnh knh kh&aacute;c  transpile/compile, k&eacute;o theo &oacute; s ho&agrave;nh h&agrave;nh ca c&aacute;c builder nh Webpack, Rollup, Parcel... L&agrave;m web vn n gin, nhng ph&aacute;t trin web ng&agrave;y nay &atilde; tr th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng vic rc ri hn bao gi ht. Bi v&igrave; s dng 1 framework ng ngha vi ri v&agrave;o m&ecirc; cung h sinh th&aacute;i bao quanh n&oacute;. Code base ng&agrave;y mt cng knh, c&nbsp;<code>npm i</code>&nbsp;ph&aacute;t l&agrave; l&ocirc;i v h&agrave;ng trm repos, h&agrave;ng chc MB source code, learning curve phc tp khin ngi s h&atilde;i...</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>8 JavaScript frameworks nh xinh</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/lr30YDJ.jpg\"><img alt=\"KISS principle\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lr30YDJ.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau &acirc;y xin gii thiu vi c&aacute;c bn 8 trong s nhiu JavaScript frameworks rt nh gn nhng kh&ocirc;ng k&eacute;m phn mnh m. Danh s&aacute;ch bao gm c 1 v&agrave;i frameworks c nhng c&ograve;n nguy&ecirc;n gi&aacute; tr tham kho i vi developer.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>1.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/jorgebucaran/hyperapp\">HyperApp</a></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><em>~1 KB minimized &amp; gzip</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Release ln u v&agrave;o 2/2/2017, micro-framework n&agrave;y v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng nh gn, hiu qu. Tuy kh&ocirc;ng phi JavaScript framework u ti&ecirc;n m&ocirc; phng kin tr&uacute;c Elm nhng HyperApp c Jorge Bucaran maintain rt tt, &atilde; c&oacute; cng ng nht nh. V2 ang ph&aacute;t trin ha hn s c&oacute; th&ecirc;m nhiu features hp dn kh&aacute;c nh Effect API, Lazy Lists, Middleware...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vi HyperApp, bn c&oacute; th khai th&aacute;c th mnh ca virtual DOM bng HyperScript t&iacute;ch hp sn hoc d&ugrave;ng JSX vi s tr gi&uacute;p ca c&aacute;c th vin nh&uacute;ng th&ecirc;m. Tt nhi&ecirc;n,  l&agrave;m 1 web app n gin th&igrave; ch cn HyperApp v&agrave;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/hyperapp/router\">HyperApp Router</a>&nbsp;l&agrave; qu&aacute; . Tng dung lng ca ch&uacute;ng khong 4KB sau minimizing v&agrave; gzip.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nu a th&iacute;ch SSR, bn cng c&oacute; th d&ugrave;ng&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/kriasoft/hyperapp-render\">hyperapp-render</a>&nbsp; x l&yacute; ng dng tr&ecirc;n Node.js server, sau &oacute; n&eacute;m HTML xung cho browser.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sample code:</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>import { h, app } from &quot;hyperapp&quot;\r\n\r\nconst state = {\r\n  count: 0\r\n}\r\n\r\nconst actions = {\r\n  down: value =&gt; state =&gt; ({ count: state.count - value }),\r\n  up: value =&gt; state =&gt; ({ count: state.count + value })\r\n}\r\n\r\nconst view = (state, actions) =&gt; (\r\n  &lt;div&gt;\r\n    &lt;h1&gt;{state.count}&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n    &lt;button onclick={() =&gt; actions.down(1)}&gt;-&lt;/button&gt;\r\n    &lt;button onclick={() =&gt; actions.up(1)}&gt;+&lt;/button&gt;\r\n  &lt;/div&gt;\r\n)\r\n\r\napp(state, actions, view, document.body)\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<h3>2.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/riot/riot\">Riot.js</a></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><em>~10 KB minimized &amp; gzip</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Riot ly cm hng WebComponent t React v&agrave; Polymer, nhng tinh gn hn rt nhiu. Th vin n&agrave;y ra i cui nm 2013, sau React v&agrave;i th&aacute;ng. Hin nay vn rt active. Hu ht issues u c gii quyt nhanh ch&oacute;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Riot cung cp cho bn custom tags, observable v&agrave; routing. Custom tags cho ph&eacute;p to ra c&aacute;c components, observable gi&uacute;p c&aacute;c components n&agrave;y giao tip vi nhau, c&ograve;n routing l&agrave;  map URL v&agrave;o component tng ng. Chng &oacute; xem nh  cho bn l&agrave;m bt c iu g&igrave; vi web apps.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ging nh React, Riot l&agrave; UI framework, kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; sn kin tr&uacute;c. Tt nhi&ecirc;n bn c&oacute; th em nhng pattern ph bin nh Redux, Flux b&ecirc;n React v&agrave;o cho Riot.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>c bit Riot h tr preprocessor, trong file components bn c&oacute; th vit script bng coffee, typescript, hoc es6; hoc thay HTML tag bng Pug syntax. Nu cn, bn c&oacute; th t&ugrave;y bin parser function  h tr th&ecirc;m c&aacute;c processor kh&aacute;c.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sample code:</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>&lt;todo&gt;\r\n  &lt;h3&gt;TODO&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n  &lt;ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;li each={ item, i in items }&gt;{ item }&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n  &lt;form onsubmit={ handleSubmit }&gt;\r\n    &lt;input ref=&quot;input&quot;&gt;\r\n    &lt;button&gt;Add #{ items.length + 1 }&lt;/button&gt;\r\n  &lt;/form&gt;\r\n\r\n  this.items = []\r\n\r\n  handleSubmit(e) {\r\n    e.preventDefault()\r\n    var input = this.refs.input\r\n    this.items.push(input.value)\r\n    input.value = &#39;&#39;\r\n  }\r\n&lt;/todo&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<h3>3.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/thysultan/dio.js\">Dio.js</a></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><em>~8.5 KB minimized &amp; gzip</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dio.js do Sultan Tarimo ph&aacute;t trin l&agrave; mt phi&ecirc;n bn thu nh ca React. Cng ging nh Preact, Dio.js c&oacute; APIs v&agrave; lifecycle methods gn tng t React, c&ugrave;ng t chc View theo components... Dio.js h tr tt SSR  bn s dng n&oacute; tr&ecirc;n Node.js server.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>T&iacute;nh cht Functional Programming v&agrave; Declarative Paradigm trong Dio.js th hin kh&aacute; r&otilde;. Hiu nng x l&yacute; ca n&oacute; cao hn Preact mt ch&uacute;t. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, framework n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; qu&aacute; nhiu t ph&aacute; v mt k thut, sc h&uacute;t ca n&oacute; k&eacute;m xa Preact.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>4.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/choojs/choo\">Choo</a></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><em>~4 KB minimized &amp; gzip</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yoshua Wuyts vit nhng d&ograve;ng code u ti&ecirc;n ca Choo v&agrave;o khong gia 2016. Th vin n&agrave;y c&oacute; built-in template helper, router, event emitter... thit k vi t tng Functional Programming v&agrave; Universal JavaScript.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nh&igrave;n code v&iacute; d ca Choo kh&aacute; ging ExpressJS vi c&aacute;c methods&nbsp;<code>use()</code>,&nbsp;<code>route()</code>&nbsp;quen thuc:</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>var html = require(&#39;choo/html&#39;)\r\nvar devtools = require(&#39;choo-devtools&#39;)\r\nvar choo = require(&#39;choo&#39;)\r\n\r\nvar app = choo()\r\napp.use(devtools())\r\napp.use(countStore)\r\napp.route(&#39;/&#39;, mainView)\r\napp.mount(&#39;body&#39;)\r\n\r\nfunction mainView (state, emit) {\r\n  return html`\r\n &lt;body&gt;\r\n &lt;h1&gt;count is ${state.count}&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n &lt;button onclick=${onclick}&gt;Increment&lt;/button&gt;\r\n &lt;/body&gt;\r\n `\r\n\r\n  function onclick () {\r\n    emit(&#39;increment&#39;, 1)\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction countStore (state, emitter) {\r\n  state.count = 0\r\n  emitter.on(&#39;increment&#39;, function (count) {\r\n    state.count += count\r\n    emitter.emit(&#39;render&#39;)\r\n  })\r\n}\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>&atilde; c&oacute; thi im Choo c u t rt chuy&ecirc;n nghip, &atilde; h&igrave;nh th&agrave;nh ng n&eacute;t ca&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/choojs/awesome-choo\">mt h sinh th&aacute;i</a>&nbsp;ln. Di sn documentation v&agrave; handbook cho thy phn n&agrave;o qu&aacute; kh huy ho&agrave;ng ngn ngi &oacute;. Hin Choo vn c maintain nhng nu kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; g&igrave; t bin xy ra, chc n&oacute; s dn ch&igrave;m v&agrave;o qu&ecirc;n l&atilde;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>5.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/MithrilJS/mithril.js\">Mithril</a></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><em>~9 KB minimized &amp; gzip</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>c maintain bi Leo Horie, mt dev ca Uber, Mithril sm g&acirc;y c n tng xut sc nh performance cao v&agrave; download size cc nh. C&oacute; sn Router v&agrave; XHR utils.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&aacute;ng tic rng kin tr&uacute;c ca Mithril c&ograve;n m h. Thc ra n&oacute; ging nh 1 bn n&acirc;ng cp ca jQuery, gia c th&ecirc;m bng virtual DOM v&agrave; two-ways data binding hn l&agrave; 1 framework ho&agrave;n thin. Bn ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n c&oacute; th d&ugrave;ng Mithril thay cho jQuery trong c&aacute;c trang web ph th&ocirc;ng, n&oacute; l&agrave;m vic rt tt vi CSS v&agrave; AJAX.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Do xut hin trc HyperApp v&agrave; AppRun nhng 2 nm n&ecirc;n Mithril c&oacute; lng contributors &ocirc;ng vt tri. Repo hin do Pat Cavit maintain, vn kh&aacute; active. Hy vng s c&oacute; nhng phi&ecirc;n bn ci tin mnh m hn trong thi gian ti.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>6.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/stasm/innerself\">innerself</a></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><em>~0.4 KB minimized &amp; gzip</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>innerself l&agrave; hin tng c &aacute;o cui 2017. N&oacute; xut hin mt c&aacute;ch t&igrave;nh c khi Sta Maolepszy, mt developer  Mozilla, l&agrave;m game tham d&nbsp;<a href=\"http://js13kgames.com/\">js13kGames</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nu nh&nbsp;<a href=\"https://js1k.com/\">js1k</a>&nbsp;t ra gii hn 1 KB cho tng dung lng code, th&igrave; js13kGames l&agrave; s&acirc;n chi ca HTML5 Game Developers c&oacute; gii hn 13 KB v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng d&ugrave;ng th&ecirc;m th vin ngo&agrave;i. iu &oacute; buc Sta Maolepszy phi to ra 1 engine nh gn. &oacute; ch&iacute;nh l&agrave;&nbsp;<code>innerself</code>&nbsp;c thit k da tr&ecirc;n m&ocirc; h&igrave;nh React + Redux.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supper mini framework n&agrave;y c&oacute; dung lng cc nh, ch khong 350 bytes sau khi optimizing. Tuy mi nhon vy nhng kin tr&uacute;c ca n&oacute; rt p.  s dng innerself, bn cng phi vit View, Reducer, np initial data v&agrave; Reducer v&agrave;o Store, ri d&ugrave;ng&nbsp;<code>dispatch</code>&nbsp; bn event + arguments t View sang cho Reducer khi cn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>S ch&uacute; &yacute; ca cng ng khin Sta Maolepszy ngc nhi&ecirc;n v&agrave; hng th&uacute;. Nhng &aacute;ng tic ch sau mt thi gian ngn, anh ta &atilde; kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n  t&acirc;m n n&oacute; na.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>D&ugrave; sao&nbsp;<code>innerself</code>&nbsp;vn  cho bn x&acirc;y dng c&aacute;c ng dng nh, ng thi em li nhiu gi&aacute; tr tham kho nu bn mun l&agrave;m ra nhng framework tng t.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>7.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/yysun/apprun\">AppRun</a></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><em>~3 KB minimized &amp; gzip</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>C&ugrave;ng tui vi HyperApp, AppRun ca Yiyi Sun cng &aacute;p dng virtual DOM v&agrave; kin tr&uacute;c Elm. Th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o &oacute; l&agrave; built-in PubSub pattern cho ph&eacute;p c&aacute;c modules tng t&aacute;c vi nhau.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Framework n&agrave;y c&oacute; performance rt tt, ngang nga HyperApp, nhng repo &iacute;t c chm ch&uacute;t v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng thu h&uacute;t c nhiu contributor. AppRun cng kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; sn routing, mc d&ugrave; bn c&oacute; th d d&agrave;ng kt hp vi c&aacute;c micro libraries chuy&ecirc;n dng nh&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/visionmedia/page.js\">page.js</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/krasimir/navigo\">navigo</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/chrisdavies/rlite\">rlite</a>...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mc nh, bn c&oacute; th d&ugrave;ng Template Literals  vit template trong view thay v&igrave; JSX. AppRun h tr tt Pure Function Component v&agrave; ang c&oacute; plan t&iacute;ch hp th&ecirc;m kh nng extend component nh class  reuse v&agrave; inherit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>C&aacute; nh&acirc;n m&igrave;nh th&iacute;ch d&ugrave;ng AppRun hn so vi c&aacute;c framework m&ocirc; phng Elm architecture kh&aacute;c. Nht l&agrave; PubSub pattern gi nh n c&aacute;c behaviors trong&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/box/t3js\">T3.js</a>&nbsp;ca Nicholas C. Zakas v&agrave;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/marionettejs/backbone.marionette\">Marionette.js</a>, 1 bin th kh&aacute; th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng tr&ecirc;n nn Backbone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sample code:</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>const state = 0;\r\nconst view = state =&gt; {\r\n  return `&lt;div&gt;\r\n    &lt;h1&gt;${state}&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n    &lt;button onclick=&#39;app.run(&quot;-1&quot;)&#39;&gt;-1&lt;/button&gt;\r\n    &lt;button onclick=&#39;app.run(&quot;+1&quot;)&#39;&gt;+1&lt;/button&gt;\r\n  &lt;/div&gt;`;\r\n};\r\nconst update = {\r\n  &#39;+1&#39;: state =&gt; state + 1,\r\n  &#39;-1&#39;: state =&gt; state - 1\r\n};\r\napp.start(&#39;my-app&#39;, state, view, update);\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<h3>8.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/radi-js/radi\">RadiJS</a></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><em>~9.3 KB minimized &amp; gzip</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Framework n&agrave;y ch mi ra i c&aacute;ch &acirc;y v&agrave;i th&aacute;ng, &iacute;t contributors nhng kh&aacute; nhiu stars. T&aacute;c gi ca n&oacute;, Mrcis Bergmanis, c&oacute; b&agrave;i &quot;<a href=\"https://medium.com/@marcisbee/how-i-built-super-fast-js-framework-faster-than-react-ea99f0d03150\">How I built super fast JS framework</a>&quot; cng g&acirc;y c ting vang nht nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Framework n&agrave;y thao t&aacute;c trc tip tr&ecirc;n real DOM thay v&igrave; virtual DOM. C&aacute;c b&agrave;i test performance ca RadiJS kh&aacute; n tng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sample code:</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>state: {\r\n  count: 0\r\n}\r\n\r\n@action change(diff) {\r\n  return {\r\n    count: this.state.count + diff\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n&lt;template&gt;\r\n  &lt;h2&gt;{ this.state.count }&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n\r\n  &lt;button\r\n    class=&quot;btn&quot;\r\n    disabled={ this.state.count &lt;= 0 }\r\n    onclick={ () =&gt; -1 |&gt; this.change }&gt;\r\n    -\r\n  &lt;/button&gt;\r\n\r\n  &lt;button\r\n    class=&quot;btn&quot;\r\n    onclick={ () =&gt; 1 |&gt; this.change }&gt;\r\n    +\r\n  &lt;/button&gt;\r\n&lt;/template&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i nhng framework k tr&ecirc;n, c&ograve;n mt s c&aacute;i t&ecirc;n &aacute;ng lu &yacute; kh&aacute;c, gm&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/Bobris/Bobril\">Bobril</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/NervJS/nerv\">Nerv</a>&nbsp;v&agrave;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/sveltejs/svelte\">Svelte</a>. Bobril v&agrave; Nerv vay mn kin tr&uacute;c t React - Reduct, nhng th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o nhiu chc nng s&aacute;ng gi&aacute; nh Fast Virtual DOM diffing, Scroll notification, Drag &amp; drop...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Svelte c&oacute; APIs kh&aacute; ging Vue, tuy nhi&ecirc;n t&aacute;c gi ca n&oacute; - Rich Harris -  cao trit l&yacute; &quot;framework without framework&quot;. &Yacute; tng ca anh l&agrave; dch source code ca chng tr&igrave;nh - bao gm framework v&agrave; code do developer vit - th&agrave;nh JavaScript thun ngay khi build, thay v&igrave; gi nguy&ecirc;n nh vy  chy l&uacute;c run (tr&ecirc;n browser). Do vy Svelte i k&egrave;m vi b build ri&ecirc;ng, cho kt qu performance rt tt, gn vi vanilla JS.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Kt lun</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>C&aacute;c frameworks c to ra  gi&uacute;p ph&aacute;t trin d &aacute;n nhanh hn. Ch&uacute;ng to ra t&iacute;nh ng b, di dng mt lp abstraction mang theo tp nguy&ecirc;n tc t chc v&agrave; thao t&aacute;c nht nh, iu n&agrave;y cho ph&eacute;p thng nht c&aacute;ch l&agrave;m vic trong c nh&oacute;m. Nhng nu d &aacute;n n gin, &iacute;t ngi l&agrave;m, th&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng nht thit phi ph thuc v&agrave;o framework. Developers cng n&ecirc;n tp sp t kin tr&uacute;c ca ri&ecirc;ng m&igrave;nh. V&agrave; c&aacute;ch tt nht l&agrave; hc hi t c&aacute;c frameworks ln nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>React, Angular, Vue... cng nh nhng ng&ocirc;i sao showbiz, s&aacute;ng ri tt, n &agrave;o n&aacute;o nhit 1 thi gian ri s b thay th bng nhng t&ecirc;n tui mi. Developer kh&ocirc;ng nht thit phi chy theo ch&uacute;ng. C hc tt 1 nhc c v&agrave; chi theo c&aacute;ch ca bn. Kh&ocirc;ng cn quan t&acirc;m nhng live show &igrave;nh &aacute;m v&agrave; thn tng ai c! Thnh thong d&otilde;i theo 1 &ocirc;ng ch&uacute; mit vn ch&egrave;o xung ba l&aacute; ca my c&acirc;u Vng c, hay lng tai nghe em g&aacute;i Kinh Bc ng&acirc;n nga &ocirc;i l&agrave;n Quan h, cng th&uacute; kh&ocirc;ng k&eacute;m &acirc;u :D</p>', '8 JS frameworks nh xinh cho bn i gi - Ho Minh Blog', '8 JS frameworks nh xinh cho bn i gi - Ho Minh Blog', '8 JS frameworks nh xinh cho bn i gi - Ho Minh Blog', '/photos/1/Test/post-default.jpg', 1, 2, 1, '2018-11-22 21:29:32', '2018-11-22 21:29:32'),
(15, 'Nhng iu vn vt ca cuc sng khng phi ai cng hiu', 'nhung-dieu-vun-vat-cua-cuoc-song-khong-phai-ai-cung-hieu', 11, 1, 'Thc ra tnh yu n th d, nhng my ai  kho lo  gi n. Gp nhau l ci duyn, ly nhau l ci phn, cn  li bn nhau l do mnh c thi.', '<p>1. C&oacute; nhng ngi bn, chi tng th&acirc;n lm ri, m&agrave; vn cha hiu nhau c my. Ch cn li&ecirc;n quan ti tin bc, bn th&acirc;n cng d th&agrave;nh ngi dng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nC&oacute; ngi, tng y&ecirc;u thng nhau nhiu lm, m&agrave; ch mt tin nhn th&ocirc;i l&agrave; ng ai ny i.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNg&agrave;y h&ocirc;m nay c&oacute; tin,  b&ecirc;n ngi n&agrave;y. Ng&agrave;y mai ht tin, mt vic,  b&ecirc;n ngi kia, hoc ch c&ograve;n li mt m&igrave;nh.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCuc i kh&oacute; lng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n2. M 50 nm cuc i n cm trng chan nc s&ocirc;i,  h&agrave;ng th&aacute;ng gi tin cho con. Con b nghin, m vn gi tin cho con, v&agrave; vn cm trng chan nc s&ocirc;i. Kh&ocirc;ng hn y&ecirc;u thng nhiu &atilde; l&agrave; tt. V&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng phi ai c&ugrave;ng bit c&aacute;ch thng ngi thng m&igrave;nh.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n3. Ai cng thay i. Mi h&ocirc;m qua c&ograve;n ngh m&igrave;nh kh&ocirc;ng th sng thiu c ngi n&agrave;y th&igrave; ba sau li &atilde;  b&ecirc;n mt ngi kh&aacute;c.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHin ti l&agrave; nh th th&igrave; bit th, v&agrave; tn hng n&oacute;. Ai bit trc ch&iacute;nh m&igrave;nh s thay i th n&agrave;o.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMt tri cng s c&oacute; ng&agrave;y tt, ch l&agrave; m&igrave;nh kh&ocirc;ng sng  l&acirc;u th nh&igrave;n thy.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"http://media.blogradio.vn//Upload/CMS/Nam_2017/Thang_3/Ngay_15/Images/nhung-dieu-vun-vat.jpg\" style=\"margin:0px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n4. Y&ecirc;u ai &oacute; ch v&igrave; n ci ca ngi &oacute;, vy th&igrave; t hn t&igrave;nh y&ecirc;u s tan v khi gp mt n ci kh&aacute;c. C&aacute;i quan trng hn l&agrave; s thu hiu, kh&ocirc;ng phi l&agrave; n ci hay m&aacute;i t&oacute;c.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n5. Hai ngi y&ecirc;u nhau, n&ecirc;n ci nhau. Hai ngi ci nhau, ri c&oacute; con. C&oacute; con ri, ch v kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n  du d&agrave;ng v&agrave; nhc nhiu n tin hn. Anh chng thy ngt ngt, ch&aacute;n v nh&agrave; v&agrave; t&igrave;m th&uacute; vui b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i. Ch v ng&agrave;y i l&agrave;m, ti chm con, mt mi v&agrave; ch&aacute;n nn v&igrave; chng v&ocirc; t&acirc;m. H chia tay.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThc ra t&igrave;nh y&ecirc;u n th&igrave; d, nhng my ai  kh&eacute;o l&eacute;o  gi n&oacute;. Gp nhau l&agrave; c&aacute;i duy&ecirc;n, ly nhau l&agrave; c&aacute;i phn, c&ograve;n  li b&ecirc;n nhau l&agrave; do m&igrave;nh c th&ocirc;i.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n6. Qu&aacute; nhiu vic kh&ocirc;ng li&ecirc;n quan n nhau v&agrave; qu&aacute; nhiu th  th&iacute;ch khin ngi ta mt mi. Chy theo nhiu mc ti&ecirc;u thc ra ch v&igrave; cha t&igrave;m ra mc ti&ecirc;u &iacute;ch thc. Bn rn nhiu khi ch l&agrave; s mt phng hng tm thi.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n7. C&oacute; ngi c i cng kh&ocirc;ng bit m&igrave;nh mun g&igrave;.  x&atilde; hi sng theo ch ngha tp th v&agrave; sng v&igrave; ng&agrave;y mai thay v&igrave; ng&agrave;y h&ocirc;m nay, ngi ta qu&ecirc;n mt m&igrave;nh n&ecirc;n sng cho c ch&iacute;nh m&igrave;nh. Ai cng nh&igrave;n ngi kh&aacute;c  sng. am m&ecirc; nhiu khi l&agrave; s xa x, hoc l&agrave; iu k cc.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n8. X&atilde; hi th&igrave; vy, nhng m&igrave;nh sng th n&agrave;o vn l&agrave; la chn ca m&igrave;nh. Kh&ocirc;ng th n&oacute;i rng t&ocirc;i phi th n&agrave;y, th kia hay ngi ta bt t&ocirc;i phi th c. Kh&ocirc;ng ai bt m&igrave;nh l&agrave;m g&igrave;, tr khi m&igrave;nh yu ui ti mc  ngi kh&aacute;c chi phi.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n9. Nhng  mnh m c th&igrave; cn c&oacute; hiu bit &atilde;. Nhm mt trc thi&ecirc;n h m&agrave; cm ci sng,  ti l&uacute;c m mt ra khi thi&ecirc;n h phi nh&igrave;n v&agrave;o m&igrave;nh. Ch ng c nh&igrave;n trc ng&oacute; sau, ri chng bao gi l&agrave;m ni iu g&igrave;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"  Nhng iu vn vt ca cuc sng khng phi ai cng hiu\" src=\"http://media.blogradio.vn//Upload/CMS/Nam_2017/Thang_3/Ngay_15/Images/dieu-vin-vat-cua-cuoc-song1.jpg\" style=\"height:483px; margin:0px; width:700px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n10. Tham lam tht ging nh ung thuc t s&aacute;t t t.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPhi chm li mt ch&uacute;t, xem c&aacute;i &oacute; c&oacute; thc s cn kh&ocirc;ng, v&agrave; nu kh&ocirc;ng l&agrave;m th&igrave; c&oacute; nh hng g&igrave; ln kh&ocirc;ng. Nhiu khi m&igrave;nh tng m&igrave;nh quan trng, nhng kh&ocirc;ng phi.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n11. Ai cng bo nhau sng n gin, kh&ocirc;ng n&ecirc;n ngh nhiu, nhng chng my ai l&agrave;m c.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nD nhi&ecirc;n l&agrave; vn c&oacute; nhng ngi chng bao gi ngh g&igrave; nhiu, nhng chc chn h vn ngh ti li &iacute;ch v&agrave; s thoi m&aacute;i ca bn th&acirc;n h. K &iacute;ch k th&igrave; sng n gin hn, k thu &aacute;o th&igrave; hay u su. Kh&ocirc;ng bit c&aacute;i n&agrave;o hn c&aacute;i n&agrave;o.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n12. ng &aacute;nh gi&aacute; ngi n&agrave;y th n&agrave;y th n khi kh&ocirc;ng bit h phi sng kh&oacute; khn hn m&igrave;nh th n&agrave;o, h phi tri qua c&aacute;i g&igrave;. M&igrave;nh n trng, c&ograve;n ngi ta phi i b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng, v&igrave; ngi ta kh&ocirc;ng may mn nh m&igrave;nh. M&igrave;nh lng 5 triu, ngi ta lng 50 triu, v&igrave; ngi ta c gng gp 10 ln m&igrave;nh.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nng thy ngi ta hn m&agrave; gh&eacute;t, ngi ta k&eacute;m m&agrave; khinh. Nu ngi ta sai m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng gi&uacute;p c th&igrave; cng n&ecirc;n im lng. S n &agrave;o c&oacute; th git cht nhng suy ngh p.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n13. Mt m&igrave;nh cng tt. Nu phi t bin m&igrave;nh th&agrave;nh k c&ocirc; c v&igrave; nhng mc &iacute;ch ln th&igrave; c l&agrave;m vy.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&aacute;m &ocirc;ng thng la h&eacute;t nhng iu kh&ocirc;ng &uacute;ng.</p>', 'Nhng iu vn vt ca cuc sng khng phi ai cng hiu - Ho Minh Blog', 'Nhng iu vn vt ca cuc sng khng phi ai cng hiu - Ho Minh Blog', 'Nhng iu vn vt ca cuc sng khng phi ai cng hiu - Ho Minh Blog', '/photos/1/nhung-dieu-vun-vat.jpg', 1, 2, 1, '2018-11-28 23:59:43', '2018-11-28 23:59:43'),
(16, 'Ra mt Laravel 5.7.14', 'ra-mat-laravel-5714', 3, 1, 'C g mi trong Laravel 5.7.14 H tr CDN asset url Trong file config/app.php gi y bn c th thm mt key...', '<p><strong>&oacute; g&igrave; mi trong Laravel 5.7.14</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>H tr CDN asset url</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong file&nbsp;<code>config/app.php</code>&nbsp;gi &acirc;y bn c&oacute; th th&ecirc;m mt key mi &oacute; l&agrave;&nbsp;<code>asset_url</code></p>\r\n\r\n<p>V&iacute; d</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>&lt;?php\r\n\r\nreturn [\r\n    ...\r\n    &#39;asset_url&#39; =&gt; &#39;https://chungnguyen.cloudimage.io&#39;,\r\n    ...\r\n];</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>th&igrave; khi gi&nbsp;<code>asset(&#39;logo.jpg&#39;)</code>&nbsp;s ra&nbsp;<code>https://chungnguyen.cloudimage.io/logo.jpg</code>&nbsp;thay v&igrave;&nbsp;<code>https://chungnguyen.xyz/logo.jpg</code></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>V&ocirc; hiu h&oacute;a Reset route</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Hin ti Laravel h tr disable route ng k&yacute; v&agrave; verify email, th&igrave; gi &acirc;y Laravel h tr th&ecirc;m v&ocirc; hiu h&oacute;a route reset password</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>Auth::routes([&#39;reset&#39; =&gt; false]);\r\n// hoc\r\nRoute::auth([&#39;reset&#39; =&gt; false]);</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Xem file:&nbsp;<code>laravel\\framework\\src\\Illuminate\\Routing\\Router.php</code>&nbsp;line 1147  bit th&ecirc;m</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>C&oacute; th ch nh TRIES v&agrave; TIMEOUT trong&nbsp;Notification</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong class Notification bn ch cn th&ecirc;m 2 thuc t&iacute;nh $tries v&agrave; $timeout l&agrave; c&oacute; th quyt nh s ln try v&agrave; thi gian timeout x l&yacute; notification &oacute;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Xem code mu</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<code>use Illuminate\\Bus\\Queueable;\r\nuse Illuminate\\Notifications\\Notification;\r\nuse Illuminate\\Contracts\\Queue\\ShouldQueue;\r\nuse Illuminate\\Notifications\\Messages\\MailMessage;\r\n\r\nclass TestNotification extends Notification implements ShouldQueue\r\n{\r\n    use Queueable;\r\n\r\n    public $tries = 3; // Max tries\r\n\r\n    public $timeout = 15; // Timeout seconds\r\n\r\n    /**\r\n     * Create a new notification instance.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return void\r\n     */\r\n    public function __construct()\r\n    {\r\n        //\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    /**\r\n     * Get the notification&#39;s delivery channels.\r\n     *\r\n     * @param  mixed  $notifiable\r\n     * @return array\r\n     */\r\n    public function via($notifiable)\r\n    {\r\n        return [&#39;mail&#39;];\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    /**\r\n     * Get the mail representation of the notification.\r\n     *\r\n     * @param  mixed  $notifiable\r\n     * @return \\Illuminate\\Notifications\\Messages\\MailMessage\r\n     */\r\n    public function toMail($notifiable)\r\n    {\r\n        return (new MailMessage)\r\n                    -&gt;line(&#39;The introduction to the notification.&#39;)\r\n                    -&gt;action(&#39;Notification Action&#39;, url(&#39;/&#39;))\r\n                    -&gt;line(&#39;Thank you for using our application!&#39;);\r\n    }\r\n}</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Illuminate\\Cookie\\CookieJar&nbsp;&rArr; macroable</h2>', 'Ra mt Laravel 5.7.14 - Ho Minh Blog', 'Ra mt Laravel 5.7.14 - Ho Minh Blog', 'Ra mt Laravel 5.7.14 - Ho Minh Blog', '/photos/1/ra-mat-laravel-5-7-15-medium.jpg', 1, 6, 1, '2018-11-30 01:39:57', '2018-11-30 01:39:57');

